Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主持正义是政府最坚定的支柱（华盛顿名言）\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The administration of justice is the firmest pillar of government.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2楼 普通庭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干得漂亮。漂亮。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You did a wonderful job. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续，你们已经听了这个漫长复杂的案子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}To continue, you've listened to a long and complex case,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一级谋杀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}murder in the first degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预谋杀人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Premeditated murder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们刑事法庭上 是刑责最重的罪名\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}is the most serious charge tried in our criminal courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都已经听过证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You've listened to the testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和适用本案的法律解释\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}had the law interpreted as it applies in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你们的职责是 坐下来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's now your duty to sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设法从想象中厘清事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and try and separate the facts from the fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人已经死了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One man is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个人命悬一线\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Another man's life is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对于被告的罪行，你们心里有一个合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If there's a reasonable doubt in your minds as to the guilt of the accused...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}a reasonable doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们就必须给我一个无罪判决\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}then you must bring me a verdict of not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无论如何没有合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And if however there's no reasonable doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你们必须，基于良知\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}then you must, in good conscience...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判决被告有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}find the accused guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论决定如何，你们的裁决必须全体一致\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}However you decide, your verdict must be unanimous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们判决被告有罪的情况下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}In the event that you find the accused guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本席将不容 任何宽大处理的建议\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the bench will not entertain a recommendation for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本案中死刑是强制性的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The death sentence is mandatory in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们面对的是一项重大的责任\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You are faced with a grave responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢，先生们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后备陪审员解散\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The alternate jurors are excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪审团现在退席\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The jury will now retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(130,128)\fs70\c&Hffffff&\fn方正黑体简体\bord0}12怒汉{\fs}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领衔主演：亨利·方达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演：西德尼·鲁迈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来块口香糖？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wanna piece of gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，谢谢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西...动不了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This thing isn't movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮把手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll give you a hand with that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今早打电话给气象局\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I called the Weather Bureau this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天将是今年中最热的一天\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is gonna be the hottest day of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本以为至少这地方有空调\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You'd think at least they'd air-condition this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字，先生?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What is your name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，是...那个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, it's...that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，先生们，大家都齐了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, gentlemen. Everybody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们需要什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, if there's anything you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在门外面，敲门就行\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll be right outside the door. Just knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从不知道他们会锁上门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I never knew they locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们当然会锁门，你以为呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure they lock the door. What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道，我只是从来没想过\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. It just never occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是要干嘛？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我以为我们可能要投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I thought we might wanna vote by ballot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意，也许我们该让他选参议员\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Great idea. Maybe we can get him elected senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得如何？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How'd you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我不知道。挺有趣的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I don't know. It was pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？我差点睡着了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah? I almost fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，我从没当过陪审员\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, I've never been on a jury before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗？我当过很多次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No? I've sat on many juries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是因为律师们说了又说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I guess it's those lawyers talk and talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是个开门见山的案子，就像这个。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}even when it's an open-and-shut case like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听过这么多没意思的话吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ever hear so much talk about nothin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他们有这个权利\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I guess they're entitled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有权利。体系是这样，不过...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They're entitled. It's the system, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我的话，我会把那些难搞的孩子扇倒\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if you ask me, I'd slap those tough kids down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们才不会惹麻烦\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}before they start any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省了我们很多时间和金钱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It saves a lot of time and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我们开始吧。可能大家都还有工作要做\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, let's get going. We've probably all got things to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们可以暂停五分钟再开始\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think we can start with a five- minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一位先生在洗手间里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's one gentleman is in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要按次序坐吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are...we gonna sit in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，我不知道。我想是吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Say, I don't know. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄，你坐到我的位置了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Buddy, you're in my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦，对不起  - 没关系\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Oh, excuse me. - That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，这风景还不错，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, that's not a bad view, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对这个案子有什么看法?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What did you think of the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，对我来说它很有意思\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, it had a lot of interest for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有真正的...死角。你明白我的意思吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No real...dead spots. You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你，遇上谋杀案算我们运气好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I tell you we were lucky to get a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我们会遇上袭击案或盗窃案\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I figured us for an assault or burglary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，那会很无聊!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, they can be the dullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，那是伍尔沃斯大楼吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, is that the Woolworth Building?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Funny
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道，我一辈子都住在这里。从没有进去过\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, I've lived here all my life. I've never been inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你必须要分辨出那些废话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If you had to sort out all that junk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟电影上的一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}like that thing with the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对。说起来，那把刀是怎么一回事?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah. Say that what about that business with the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，要成年人去相信那种胡话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, asking grown-up people to believe that kind of jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，你指望那个。你知道我们在对付什么。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Truly, you expect that. You know what we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我想是这样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的喇叭能用了，现在试试你的灯光吧。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, your horn works. Now try your lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么，你感冒了?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What're you, got a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有热。这热感冒真是要命\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And hot. This hot-weather colds can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我简直不能碰我的鼻子，知道我的意思吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I can hardly touch my nose. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然。我感冒才刚好。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure do. I just got over one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，快点！主席先生，咱们开始吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, come on! Mr Foreman, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还在洗手间里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The guy's still in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么新闻？我今早没机会看报纸\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's new? I didn't get a chance to see a paper this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道今天收盘的情况。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was only wondering how the market closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有交易席位吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You got a seat on the exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个经纪人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm a broker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经营通信业务\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I run a messenger service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝克传呼公司\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The Beck and Call Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是我妻子取的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The name is my wife's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有37个人干活。白手起家。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Got 37 men workin'. Started with nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，各位。咱们找座位吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, men. Let's take our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都能很快离开这里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can all get out of here pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你们其他人怎样。但我有今晚球赛的票。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know about the rest of you. But I have tickets to that ball game tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋基对克利夫兰。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yanks and Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有这个叫摩杰维斯基的小子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We've got this kid Modjelewski in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是头公牛，这小子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's a real bull, this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的接球手。你知道吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Real jug-handled. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个棒球迷，是吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're a real baseball fan, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要坐在哪里?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where do we sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们照次序坐，你知道，按陪审员编号。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I thought we'd sit in order, you know, by jury numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一、二、三、四、五  以此类推围着桌子坐\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One, two, three, four, five and so on around the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们各位没意见的话。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if that's OK with you gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那有什么差别?  - 按次序坐挺合理的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What's the difference? - It's reasonable to sit in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就这么办吧  - 这是十二号\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Let it be. - That's twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你开始一  二\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We go around one, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对公诉检察官的印象如何?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What was your impression of the prosecuting attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I beg pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他很尖锐\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I thought he was really sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他处理那些论点的方式 一个接一个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the way he handled all those points one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照逻辑顺序\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}in logical sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我印象深刻\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他，干得非常专业\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think he...he did an expert job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很能驾驭。知道吗，真正的驾驭\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A lot of drive, too. You know? Real drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，大伙儿。咱们能安静会儿吗？大家？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, fellas. Can we hold it down a minute? Fellas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，我们就要开始了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Say, we'd like to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户旁边的先生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Gentleman at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们就要开始了  - 哦，我很抱歉。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- We'd like to get started. - Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难理解，对吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pretty tough to figure, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子杀了他的父亲，砰，就那样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid kills his father, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，你用我的眼光来看，就能看到这种事常见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, you have my eyes to figure, you'll see it happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你，他们由着那些孩子在外面野\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm telling you they let those kids run wild up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这是他的报应，明白我意思吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, maybe serves him right. you know what i mean
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都到了吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人还在里面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 麻烦你敲门叫他好吗?  - 好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Would you knock on the door for him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是洋基队的球迷吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are you a Yankee fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。巴尔的摩队\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, Baltimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔的摩队?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Baltimore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就像是每天头上被铁橇敲一次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's like being hit in the head with a crowbar once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who have they got?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了有个不错的外野手，他们还有谁？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who have they got besides good groundkeepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，我们要开始了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Say, we'd like to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，原谅我，先生们，我不是故意要你们等着。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Forgive me, gentlemen. I didn't mean to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔的摩队!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Baltimore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，先生们，请注意。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, gentlemen, if I can have your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要怎么做这事都可以\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You fellas can handle this thing any way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不打算定什么规则\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm...you know, I'm not gonna make any rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以...先讨论，再来表决\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can, well, discuss it first, then vote on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样，当然，是一种方法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's, of course... that's one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有，我们也可以立刻进行表决\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And, well, we can vote on it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想，习惯上，要来一次初步投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think it's customary to take a preliminary vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我们来投票吧，谁知道呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, let's vote. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们都可以离开这里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe we can all get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，那么...我想你们都知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. Then I think that you know that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这是一桩一级谋杀的指控\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}we have a first-degree murder charge here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们投票被告有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and if we vote the accused guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就得送他上电椅\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}we've got to send him to the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是强制的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们知道这点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think we know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，来看看大家的立场\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, let's see who's where.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，有人不想进行表决吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Okay, anyone doesn't wanna vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没意见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，那么请记住...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, then, just remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须是12比0，不管怎么判。那是法律\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}this has to be twelve to nothing, either way. That's the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们准备好了吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, are we ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有投有罪的，请举手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now all those voting guilty, please raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One, two, three, four, five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八  九  十  十一\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}eight, nine, ten, eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，十一个 有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, that's eleven guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投无罪票的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Those voting not guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一票。好的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一票有罪，一票无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Eleven guilty, one not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们知道进展到哪了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, now we know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊，好啊，总是有那么一个。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, oh boy! There's always one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们现在干什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我猜我们讨论。  - 好啊好啊。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- I guess we talk. - Boy, oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的觉得他是无辜的?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You really think he's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐在法庭里，跟我们一样，\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You sat in court with the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到的跟我们一样。那孩子是个危险的杀手，看得出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You heard what we did. The kid's a dangerous killer. You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他十八岁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够大了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, that's old enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刀刺自己的父亲 胸口4英寸深\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He stabbed his own father four inches into the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在法庭上 以多种不同方式证明了这点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They proved it a dozen different ways in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我给你列个清单吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Would you like me to list 'em for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想怎么样?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Then what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想谈一谈\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可谈的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's there to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们十一个人认为他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Eleven of us think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人需要第二次考虑，除了你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No one had to think about it twice except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问问你。你相信他的说词吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I want to ask you something. Do you believe his story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道信还是不信，或许我不相信\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know whether I believe or not. Maybe I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么投无罪票？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So how come you voted not guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有十一个投有罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There were eleven votes for guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要举起我的手送一个孩子去死并不容易\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not easy to raise my hand and send a boy off to die
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不先讨论一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}without talking about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谁说这容易了？ - 没人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Well, now, who says it's easy? - No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？就因为我投票快吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What? Just because I voted fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心认为那家伙有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I honestly think the guy is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能改变我的想法，即便谈上一百年。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Couldn't change my mind if you talked for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想改变你的想法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm not trying to change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...我们谈的是某人的生命。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's just that... We're talking about somebody's life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能在五分钟里就决定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can't decide in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设我们错了呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposing we're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“假设我们错了”？假设这整栋房子倒在我头上？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}'Supposing we're wrong' Supposing this whole building fell on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以假设任何事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can suppose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花多少时间有什么差别？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the difference how long it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设我们花五分钟，为什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposin' we take five minutes, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们花一小时\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's take an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球赛八点才会开始\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The ball game doesn't start till eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要说什么吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who's got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意坐一小时\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm willing to sit for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了。我昨晚听见一个精彩故事...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Great. I heard a pretty good story last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我们坐在这里的原因。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's not why we're sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。那你告诉我，我们坐在这里干什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right, then you tell me. What are we sitting here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。或许没有原因\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. Maybe no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，这孩子一生被踢来踢去。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, this kid's been kicked around all over his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道，贫民窟出生，九岁时母亲死了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, born in a slum, mother dead since he was nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在孤儿院待过一年半\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He lived for a year and a half in an orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他父亲因为伪造罪入狱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}when his father was serving a jail term for forgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是什么好的开端\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's not a very happy beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个愤怒的野孩子。一直如此。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's a wild, angry kid. That's all he's ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道原因吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为天天都有人打他的头\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Cos he's been hit on the head by somebody once a day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他过了悲惨的十八年\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's had a pretty miserable 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得我们欠他一点言辞，就这样。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I...I just think we owe him a few words, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意告诉你，先生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't mind telling you this, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么都不欠他，他得到公平的审判，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We don't owe him a thing. He got a fair trial, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为那场审判花了多少钱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think that trial cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到这个他是走运了。懂我的意思吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's lucky he got it. Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，这里大家都是成年人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, we're all grown-ups in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听到了事实， 对吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We heard the facts, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要告诉我说我们应该相信那孩子吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna tell me we're supposed to believe this kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道他是什么样的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}knowing what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，我一辈子在他们中间生活。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've lived among them all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说的一句也不能信。你知道的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can't believe a word they say. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思，他们天生就是骗子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, they're born liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有无知的人才会相信那些话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Only an ignorant man can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 听着  - 你认为自己天生就垄断了真理吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Now, listen... - Do you think you were born with a monopoly on the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为必须向这个人指出某些事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Certain things should be pointed out to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，今天不是礼拜天。我们不需要训诫\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, this's not Sunday. We don't need a sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，我们有工作要做。快干吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, we have a job to do. Now let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆米花。是我代理的一个产品\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Rice Pops. It's a product I work on at the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"天生充满活力的早餐"\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"The breakfast with the built-in bounce."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写的台词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I wrote that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 非常有感染力  - 没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Very catchy. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我说，你不介意吧？  - 对不起\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Say, do you mind? - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有随手涂鸦的习惯，能让我理清思路\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have this habit of doodling. It keeps me thinking clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，我们还有事要做\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ya, we have all this work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耗在这里没有意义\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's no point staying here for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。也许那边的那位先生...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. Perhaps if the gentleman down there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不同意我们的那位\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}who is disagreeing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以说说为什么，让我们知道你的想法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}...perhaps you could say why. Tell us what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们就能告诉你你哪里弄错了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We might be able to show you where you're mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能是个办法。我对这事并没有想太多\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, maybe this is an idea. I haven't given it much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我看来，似乎我们得说服这位先生：\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It seems to me that it's up to us to convince him that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他错了，我们是对的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he's wrong and we're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们每个人都花几分钟的时间  好好地...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe if we each took a couple of minutes just to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个不成熟的办法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, it was just a quick idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，办法很好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, no, no. That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不妨照座位顺序依次来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposing we go once around the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你是第一个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I guess you're first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很难用语言表达\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's hard to put into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想从一开始就很明显\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I thought it was obvious from the word go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说没有人证明另一面（无罪）\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean nobody proved otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人需要去证明另一面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody has to prove otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举证责任在于公诉人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The burden of proof's on the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被告甚至不必开口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The defendant doesn't even have to open his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是写在宪法里的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's in the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，当然，我知道。但我的意思是\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure, I know that. What I meant was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I just think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，有人看到他干了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, somebody saw him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。这是我的想法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. Here's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我对此没有个人感情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And I have no personal feelings about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想讨论事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just wanna talk about facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在楼下的那老人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man lived downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在凶案现场房间的下方\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}under the room where the killing took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在凶案发生当晚的十二点十分\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}At 10 minutes after 12 on the night of the killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他听到很大的声音。说听起来像是争吵\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he heard loud noises. Said it sounded like a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他听到那孩子大叫："我要杀了你"\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And he heard the kid yell out "I'm gonna kill ya."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒钟后他听见人体撞在地板上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A second later, he heard a body hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到门口，打开门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ran to the door, opened it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那孩子冲下楼梯离开房子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}saw the kid run down the stairs and out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报警\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们进去，发现那老子胸口插了一把刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They came in found the old man with the knife in his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法医推测死亡时间大约是午夜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The coroner fixed the time of death around midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, these are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法反驳事实。那孩子有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can't refute facts. The kid is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟旁边的人一样有同情心\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm just as sentimental as the next fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他只有18岁，但...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I know he's only 18, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是得为自己的作为付出代价\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he's still gotta pay for what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一边\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。你说完了吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 下一位\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Yeah. - Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样，对我来说很明显，那男孩的整篇说辞都是瞎编\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It is obvious to me anyway that the boy's entire story was flimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他声称凶杀发生时他在看电影\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He claimed he was at the movies during the time of killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而一小时后他想不起看的电影名字或是谁演的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}yet he couldn't remember the names of the films he saw or who played in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没错  - 而且没人见过他进出电影院\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- That's right. - And no one saw him at the theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，对街的那个女人怎么样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, what about the woman across the street
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她的证词都不能证明，那就没有别的了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if her testimony don't prove it, nothing does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，她是实际看到凶杀的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right. She was the one who actually saw the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴们，拜托，我们照顺序来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Fellas, please. Let's go in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个女人...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here's a woman。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个女人躺在床上。她睡不着。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here's a woman who's lying in bed. She can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她热得受不了，你们知道我的意思吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She's dyin' with the heat. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正，她从窗户往外看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyway, she looks out the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好隔着街道 她看到那孩子刀刺他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and right across the street she sees the kid stick the knife into his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间正好是12:10\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The time is 12:10 on the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样样都符合，瞧，那孩子从小她就认识\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Everything fits. Look, she's known the kid all his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的窗户跟她的正隔一条电车轨道。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}His window is opposite hers across the el tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她发誓她看见他干的事情。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She swore she saw him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一列电车经过窗前。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Through the windows of a passing el train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这辆电车上没有乘客。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This el train had no passengers on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正要开到市区去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was just being moved downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯没开，记得吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The lights were out, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在法庭上证明了：\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and they proved in court that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上灯没开的时候，你可以透过车窗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}at night you can look through the windows when lights were out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到另一边发生的事情。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and see what's happening on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们证明过。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They proved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你一点事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不相信那孩子的说法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You don't believe the boy's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会相信这个女人的呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How come you believe the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是“他们”中的一个，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She's one of "them" too, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个聪明人，是吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're a pretty smart fella, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，先生们。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, gentlemen. Now, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，坐下，坐下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他显什么聪明？我告诉你...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's he so wise about? I'm telling you..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。我们现在不是要吵架\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on. Now we're not gonna get anywhere fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个轮到谁了？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Whose turn is it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，到他，五号\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, his. Number five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，我可以弃权吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}May I... Can I pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那，那是你的权利\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well... That's your privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位先生呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How about the next gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。一开始我就被说服了，你知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh. Well...I don't know. I started to be convinced, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在审案很早的时候\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}very early in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看，我在寻找动机\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You see, I was looking for a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很重要，因为...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's very important because
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有动机，就没有案子，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if you don't have a motive, where's your case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，那些人的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyway, that testimony from those people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在那孩子公寓过道对门的那些人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the apartment across the hall from the kid's apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证词很有力\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}that was very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是提到过一次吵架，一次争论吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Didn't they say something about a fight, an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老子和儿子之间，就在那天晚上约七点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}between the old man and his son around about seven o'clock that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说或许我错了，但...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mena I could be wrong but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是八点，不是七点  - 没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- It was eight o'clock, not seven. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们听到了争吵\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They heard an argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不清楚在吵什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}couldn't hear about what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他们听到那父亲打了那男孩两下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Then they heard the father hit the boy twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后他们看到那男孩愤怒地冲出家门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Finally they saw the boy run, angry, out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那能证明什么呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What does that prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不能实际证明什么。那只是事情的一部份\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It don't prove anything. It's just part of the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那证明了动机\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You said it provided a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公诉人也这么说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The prosecution said the samething
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这不是个很强的动机\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think it was a very strong motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这男孩生活中被打过太多次，暴力实际上...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This boy has been hit so many times that violence is practically...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他是平常事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's a normal state of affairs with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不出被打了两个耳光会刺激他预谋杀人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just can't see two slaps in the face provoking him into committing murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许那两下就是过多了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It may have been two too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有个爆发点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Everyone has a breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没有了  - 好。你呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- No. - OK. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。都说过了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. It's all been said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以永远说下去。还是一回事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can talk here for ever. It's still the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子是5比0\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This kid is five for 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他的记录\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, look at his record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他十岁就进了少年法庭\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When he was 10, he was in children's court:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他朝老师扔石头\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He threw a rock at a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五岁时 进教管所\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When he was 15, he was in reform school:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷了一辆车\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He stole a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾因抢劫被捕\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's been arrested for muggin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾因持刀械斗被抓两次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was picked up twice for knife fightin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说他真的很会用刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They say he's real handy with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，这可是个非常不错的男孩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, this is a very fine boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他五岁大时开始\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ever since he was five years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父亲就时时揍他。用拳头。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}his father beat him up regularly. He used his fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会的。像那样的孩子？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So would I. A kid like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子就是这样的，现如今。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's these kids-the way they are nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候，称我父亲为“先生”。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When I was a kid, I used to call my father "sir".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错。“先生”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right. 'sir'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听过哪个孩子那样称呼他父亲吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ever hear a kid call his father that any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作父亲的似乎也不觉得这很重要了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Fathers don't seem to think it's important any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有孩子吗?  - 三个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- You got any kids? - Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十二岁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}22 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他九岁时，打架逃跑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When he was nine years old, he ran away from a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了，觉得太丢脸\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I saw it. I was so embarrassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点吐出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I almost threw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说"我要把你变成一个男子汉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I said "I'm gonna make a man out of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我得把你劈成两半。"\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if I have to break you in two tryin'."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好么，我把他打造成个男子汉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I made a man out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他十六岁时，我们打了一架\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When he was 16, we had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了我的下巴。他是个高大的孩子。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hit me in the jaw. He was a big kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两年没有见到他了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I haven't seen him for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呕心沥血...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You work your heart out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们继续吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, let's get goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们忘了重点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think we're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男孩，这么说吧，是破碎家庭的产物\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This boy, let's say he's the product of a broken home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自污秽的社区。这我们爱莫能助\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and a filthy neighbourhood. We can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来这里决定他有没有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're here to decide his innocence or guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要探究他为何长成这样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}not to go into the reasons why he grew up the way he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出生于贫民窟\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was born in a slum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贫民窟是犯罪的温床。我知道，你们也知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Slums are breeding grounds for criminals. I know it and so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是秘密，来自贫民窟的孩子对社会是潜在的威胁。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's no secret that children from slums are potential menaces to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想...  - 兄弟，这话你可以再说一次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Now I think... - You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那些地方爬出来的孩子真是垃圾\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kids who crawl out of these places are real trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟他们沾边，告诉你们...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't want any part of them, I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，我一生都住在贫民窟里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, I...I've lived in a slum all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 等一下  - 拜托，我...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Wait a minute. - Please. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾在堆满垃圾的脏后院里玩耍，我是说...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've played in back yards that were filled with garbage. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你还可以在我身上闻到那股味。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe you can still smell it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，小伙子...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now listen, sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 得了。这不是私人恩怨  - 可这是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Come on, now. There's nothing personal. - But there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，伙计。他说的不是你。咱们别那么敏感\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, fella. He didn't mean you. Let's not be so sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉我能理解。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This sensitivity I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。咱们别吵了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, look. Let's stop the arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是在浪费时间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're only wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到你那边了。我们继续。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, your turn down there. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到轮到我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I didn't expect a turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你们都要来说服我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I thought you were all gonna to try to convince me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个办法吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wasn't that the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对，是这个办法。  - 我忘了这事了。他是对的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Check, that was the idea. - I forget about that. He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么区别？是他把我们留在这里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What difference does it make? He's the one keeping us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们听听他要说什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's hear what he's got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，等等。我们已经决定按一定的办法来。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, no, wait a minute, wait. We decided to do this a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该遵循下去。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think we ought to stick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，别孩子气了，行吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, stop being a kid, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么意思？孩子气\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我什么意思？孩-子-气\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think I mean? K-I-D: Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，就因为我尽量保持这事有秩序...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, just because I'm trying to keep this organised
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，你来接，你接下这个责任\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here, you take it. You take this on the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以闭嘴，就这样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll just keep my mouth shut. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么这么上火？冷静点，行吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why are you gettin' so hot? Calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我冷静\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't tell me to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，你想当主席？来当主席吧，就这样。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, you want to take the chair? Take the chair. Just take the chair, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看过这种事吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Did you ever see such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，你觉得很有趣吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, you think it's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧，伙计，这事情不重要。来吧。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Forget it, fella. The whole thing is unimportant. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不重要？来，你来试试\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Unimportant? Here, you try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，没人想改变\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, nobody wants to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的非常好。请坐\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're doing a beautiful job. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，你做得很好。很好，伙计\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, you're doin' great. Just great, fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐在那，你发球\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You stay in there and pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，我们来听听别人的说法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right, let's hear from somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们要我说出我的感觉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, if you want me to tell you how I feel about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么问题\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}it's all right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，我不在乎你做什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, I don't care what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。我没有什么高明之处\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. I don't have anything brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的跟你们一样多\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I only know as much as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据证词，那男孩看来是有罪的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}According to the testimony, the boy looks guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他是\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.74,0:24:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六天来我坐在法庭上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I sat there in court for six days
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着证据构建起来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}listening while the evidence built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都说得如此肯定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Everybody sounded so positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始对这次审判有了特别的感觉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, I began to get a peculiar feeling about this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.95,0:24:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是，没有什么事情能那么肯定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, nothing is that positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些问题我想要提出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There are questions I'd have liked to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道，或许它们毫无意义，但是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know, maybe they wouldn't mean anything but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.09,0:24:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始感觉辩方并没有执行足够彻底的交叉讯问\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I felt that the defence wasn't conducting a thorough enough cross-examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.66,0:24:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他放过了太多的小细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He let too many things go by-little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么小细节?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What little things?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.33,0:24:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，这些家伙不提出问题。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, when these fellos don't ask questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.02,0:24:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为他们已经盘算出答案不利。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}it's because they know the answers already they figured out be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许可能是因为那律师...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe it's also possible for a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.89,0:24:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是个笨蛋，对吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to be just plain stupid, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.91,0:24:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，那是有可能的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来你曾见过我的小舅子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You sound like you met my brother-in-law once.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.95,0:25:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直把自己放在那孩子的位置\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I kept putting myself in the kid's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.15,0:25:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会要求换一个律师，我觉得\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd have asked for another lawyer, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.06,0:25:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，如果这场审判关乎我的生命\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, if I was on trial for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想要我的律师粉碎公诉人的证人证据\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd want my lawyer to tear the prosecution witnesses to shreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他该尽力\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}or at least try to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.97,0:25:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，这件凶案有一个所谓的目击证人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, there was one alleged eyewitness to this killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.41,0:25:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一个人声称听到凶案\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Someone else claims he heard the killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.47,0:25:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那男孩后来跑出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}saw the boy run out afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多间接证据\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and there was circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上那两个证人就是公诉人的全部依据\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But actually those two witnesses were the entire case for the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设他们都错了呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposing they're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.54,0:25:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么意思，假设他们错了？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean, supposing they're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.31,0:25:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要证人的意义何在？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the point of having witnesses at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.45,0:25:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会不会犯错？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Could they be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.18,0:25:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么？那些人都发过誓\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What're you trying to say? Those people were under oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.02,0:25:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只是人。人难免会犯错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They're only people. People make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.48,0:25:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会不会犯错？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Could they be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.99,0:25:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不。我不那么认为  - 你了解吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Well, no. I don't think so. - Do you know so?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，没有人可以了解那种事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, come on. Nobody can know a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.82,0:25:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是精密科学。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This isn't an exact science.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.54,0:25:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，它不是。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们来谈要点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, let's get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.79,0:25:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把折叠刀怎么回事？他们发现插在老子的胸口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about the switch knife they found in the old man's chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.25,0:26:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，有人还没有发言\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Some people haven't talked yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.20,0:26:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不该照顺序来吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Shouldn't we go in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会有机会说话，安静一会儿好吗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They'll get a chance to talk. Be quiet a second, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.75,0:26:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀怎么样呢？这个正直的好男孩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about the knife this fine, upright boy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.74,0:26:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认是在凶杀当晚买的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}admitted buying the night of the killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.70,0:26:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来谈谈它\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我们谈谈它。我们把它拿进来看看。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. Let's get it in here and look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.51,0:26:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再看看它。主席先生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to see it again. Mr.Foreman?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.26,0:26:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都看过它的样子，为什么还要再看？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We all saw what it looks like. Why do we have to see it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生有权利要求审视证物\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The gentleman has a right to see exhibits in evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我说，你能把那把刀拿来吗？  - 那把刀？好。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Say, could you bring us the knife? - The knife? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.57,0:26:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀以及它是如何被购买的 是相当有力的证据\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The knife and the way it was bought is pretty strong evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.23,0:26:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.95,0:26:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我觉得是  - 很好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- I do. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.64,0:26:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我们一样样来检视事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now suppose we take the facts one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.30,0:26:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一：那男孩承认谋杀那晚在八点钟离开家\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One: The boy admitted leaving the house at eight o'clock at night
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被他父亲打了几下耳光后\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}after being slapped several times by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.71,0:26:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，他没说"被打耳光"\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, he didn't say "slapped".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.51,0:26:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他"拳打"。耳光和拳打是不一样的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said "punched". There's a difference between slap and punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.75,0:26:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被他父亲打了几下后\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}After being hit several times by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.57,0:26:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二：他直接跑到附近一家旧货店买了一把那种...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Two: He went directly to a local junk shop where he bought one of those...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.49,0:26:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 折叠刀  - 弹簧折刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Switch knives. - Switchblade knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.13,0:26:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一把你们说的普通刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This wasn't what you call an ordinary knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.92,0:27:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀柄刻花和刀锋很不寻常\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It had a very unusual carved handle and blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.94,0:27:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖给他的店主说他的店里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The storekeeper said it was the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的刀一向只有这一把\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}of its kind he had ever had in stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.57,0:27:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三：8:45左右他在一家酒吧前遇到一些朋友\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Three: He met some friends of his in front of a tavern about 8.45.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.41,0:27:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止我说的都对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Am I right so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.95,0:27:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是，对的  - 他一点都没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Yes, you are. - You bet he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.21,0:27:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟他的朋友聊了一小时\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He talked with his friends for an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.61,0:27:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在9:45时离开\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}leaving them at 9.45.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.48,0:27:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这段时间里，他们看到了那折叠刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}During this time, they saw the switch knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四：他们在法庭指认那个致死武器\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Four: They identified the death weapon in court
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.66,0:27:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那把刀非常相似\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}as that very same knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.16,0:27:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五：大约十点时他回到家里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Five: He arrived home at about ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.20,0:27:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里公诉机关跟那男孩的说词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is where the stories offered by the State
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.17,0:27:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始出现微小分歧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and the boy diverge slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他声称他在11:30出去看电影\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He claims that he went to a movie at about 11.30
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3:10回到家 发现父亲死了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}returning home at 3.10 to find his father dead
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.25,0:27:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他遭到逮捕\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and himself arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还声明逮捕他的两名探员...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He also claims that the two detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.43,0:27:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他丢下半截楼梯\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}threw him down a half a flight of stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.98,0:27:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那把折叠刀怎么样了呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now what happened to the switch knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他声称从口袋的破洞掉了出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He claims it fell through a hole in his pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.84,0:27:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去看电影的路上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}on the way to the movies
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11:30到3:10之间的某个时候\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}sometime between 11.30 and 3.10,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.53,0:27:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后他再也没有看到它\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and that he never saw it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个说法，先生们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, there is a tale, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.31,0:27:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为很清楚 那晚上那男孩没有去看电影\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think it's quite clear the boy never went to the movies that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.86,0:28:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房子里没有一个人看到他11:30出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No one in the house saw him go out at 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.97,0:28:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影院没有一个人认出他\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No one at the theatre identified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.83,0:28:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至不记得看的那部电影的名字\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He couldn't even remember the names of the pictures he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.70,0:28:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的发生的是，那男孩待在家里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What actually happened is this. The boy stayed home
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他父亲再次争吵\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}had another fight with his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.77,0:28:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺死了他，在十二点十分离家\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}stabbed him to death and left the house at 10 minutes after 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.55,0:28:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至记得擦净刀上的指纹\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He even wiped the knife clean of fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.58,0:28:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，你是想告诉我 这把刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, are you trying to tell me that this knife
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的从那男孩口袋的洞掉出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}really fell through a hole in the boy's pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.39,0:28:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在街上捡起它 跑到那男孩家\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}someone picked it up off the street, went to the boy's house
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.46,0:28:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它刺死他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and stabbed his father with it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.96,0:28:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了测试它的锋利度？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}just to test its sharpness?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.33,0:28:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我只是说有可能那男孩丢了他的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, I'm just saying it's possible the boy lost his knife
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.70,0:28:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另有别人用类似的刀杀了他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and somebody else stabbed his father with a similar knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.91,0:28:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是可能\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's just possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.01,0:28:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这把刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Take a look at this knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.73,0:28:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一把非常不寻常的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's a very unusual knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.90,0:28:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有看过这样的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've never seen one like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.49,0:28:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它卖给那男孩的店主也没有\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Neither had the storekeeper who sold it to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.47,0:28:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想让我们接受难以置信的巧合吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Aren't you asking us to accept an pretty incredible coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.64,0:28:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说 巧合是可能的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm just saying a coincidence is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.73,0:28:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我说不可能\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And I say it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.85,0:29:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西从哪里来的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一样的刀！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's the same knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.29,0:29:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己在做什么?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think you're doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.94,0:29:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪里弄来的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.56,0:29:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚出去散了几个小时步\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I went out walking for a couple of hours last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.82,0:29:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经过那孩子住的社区\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I walked through the boy's neighbourhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一家当铺买下它 离那男孩家只有两个街区远\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I bought that at a pawn shop just two blocks from the boy's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.14,0:29:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,价值六元钱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It cost six dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.28,0:29:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买或者卖弹簧折刀是违法的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's against the law to buy or sell switchblade knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.37,0:29:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错。我犯了法。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right. I broke the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.74,0:29:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好，你耍了高明的一招\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, you pulled a real bright trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设你告诉我这证明了什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now supposing you tell me what it proves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.08,0:29:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还有十把类似的刀，又怎样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe there are ten knives like that, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是有！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.25,0:29:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到一把类似的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You found a knife like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.63,0:29:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算什么？世纪大发现还是什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's that? The discovery of the age or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我们相信 另有别人用完全一样的刀杀人？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You mean you're asking us to believe that somebody else did the stabbing with exactly the same kind of knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机率是百万比一。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The odds are a million to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.46,0:29:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这种机会!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.90,0:29:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是很可能。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But not very probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.33,0:29:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，伙伴们，我们坐回原位\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, fellas. Let's take our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.12,0:29:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处乱站没什么意义\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's no point standing around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.80,0:29:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧真有趣，他能找到跟那男孩卖的完全一样的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know it's interesting that he'd find a knife exactly like the one the boy bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.57,0:29:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么趣？有趣！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's interesting about it? Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.01,0:29:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道，我就是觉得有趣\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I don't know. I just thought it was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.35,0:29:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里还是有十一个人认为他有罪。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There're still eleven of us here think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.57,0:30:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对。你认为你能达成什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right. What do you thinke you're gonna accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.58,0:30:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会改变任何人的想法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna change anybody's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.39,0:30:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要是你想拖着这个陪审团，请便。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So, if you wanna hang this jury, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.93,0:30:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子会再次受审，被判有罪，就像他出生那样确定。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid'll be tried again and found guilty, as sure as he's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.69,0:30:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你说的对\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.23,0:30:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你打算怎么做呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.26,0:30:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以一整晚都在这里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can be here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.58,0:30:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一夜。一个男孩可能会死。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's only one night. A boy may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.13,0:30:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好么，我们干吗不在这里成立家庭呢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, why don't we just set up house here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫人去拿副牌来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Someone send for a pinochle deck
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就好好乐一乐\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and we'll just sweat the whole thing out right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.24,0:30:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他不该拿这事开玩笑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think he oughta joke about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.15,0:30:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我怎么做?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.38,0:30:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，听着，我看不出这把该死的刀有什么关系。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, listen, I don't see what all this god damn knife has got to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.92,0:30:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人看见那孩子刺了他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Somebody saw the kid stab his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要别的吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What more do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.03,0:30:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以说掉我的耳朵，知道我的意思吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You guys can talk the ears right off my head. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.09,0:30:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说话的时候 我有三家汽修厂要破产了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I got three garages going to pot while you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快把事情办好离开这里吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So let's get done and get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.77,0:30:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对地区检察官来说那把刀很重要  他花了一天...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The knife was important to the district attorney. He spent a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.66,0:30:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个第15助理什么的。这事他懂什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's a 15th assistant or something. What does he know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.65,0:30:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们小声点，这方面的争吵只能拖慢我们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's hold it down. These side arguments are only slowin' us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.41,0:31:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢？你是唯一一个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, what about it? You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.15,0:31:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个提议给你们大家\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have a proposition to make to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.25,0:31:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要再投一次票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm going to call for another vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.56,0:31:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你们十一个人...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I want you eleven men to...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.31,0:31:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书面秘密投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}vote by secret written ballot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.98,0:31:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会放弃的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll abstain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.64,0:31:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有十一张投有罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If there are eleven votes for guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.83,0:31:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会固执己见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I won't stand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.61,0:31:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以立刻向法官提出有罪判决\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We'll take in a guilty verdict to the judge right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.04,0:31:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要有任何一个投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But if anyone votes not guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.05,0:31:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就待在这里谈清楚\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}we'll stay here and talk it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.28,0:31:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样。如果你们想试试，我准备好了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's it. If you want to try it, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.98,0:31:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。我们受点累。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. Let's do it the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.62,0:31:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很公平。大家都同意吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That sounds fair. Everyone agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.56,0:31:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 有人反对吗？ - 很好，我们来。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyone doesn't agree? -Fine, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.75,0:31:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，把这传下去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, pass these along.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.89,0:32:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.10,0:32:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.67,0:32:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.30,0:32:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.44,0:32:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.64,0:32:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.01,0:32:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.35,0:32:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.25,0:32:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.29,0:32:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.79,0:32:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊，怎么能这样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, how do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.75,0:33:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一个小子乍翅了！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And another chap flips his wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.33,0:33:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，是谁？来啊，我想知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. Who was it? Come on, I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起。这是秘密投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Excuse me. This was a secret ballot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.22,0:33:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都同意的，不是吗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We all agreed on that, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.10,0:33:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这位先生想保持秘密\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If the gentleman wants it to remain secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.21,0:33:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密？你是什么意思？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Secret? What do you mean secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪审团室里没有秘密\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There are no secrets in a jury room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道是谁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I know who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.13,0:33:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟，你可真行。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Brother, you really are somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.11,0:33:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐在这里，和我们一样投有罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You sit here vote guilty like the rest of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.38,0:33:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着某个金嗓子的牧师 说得你心碎\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}then some golden-voiced preacher tears your poor heart out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.85,0:33:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么一个社会底层的孩子 不可避免沦为杀人犯\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}about some underprivileged kid couldn't help becoming a murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.03,0:33:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是你改了投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and you change your vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.02,0:33:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的最让人厌恶...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If that isn't the most sickening...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.89,0:33:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不扔个铜板到他的募捐箱里？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why don't you drop a quarter in his collection box?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.53,0:33:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, now just wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.57,0:33:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，你不能那样子跟我说话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, you can't talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.43,0:33:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.60,0:33:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点，这没关系\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Calm down, calm down. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.21,0:33:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很容易激动。快坐下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's very excitable. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.87,0:33:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激动？我就是容易激动!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Excitable? You bet I'm excitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.83,0:33:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把一个有罪的人送上电椅，他活该\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're tryin' to put a guilty man in the chair, where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人开始跟我们讲童话，我们就听了！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Someone starts tellin' us fairy tales and we're listenin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.74,0:33:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，你，算了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, you...Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么让你改变投票？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What made you change your vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.53,0:33:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有改投票。我改的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He didn't change his vote. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.25,0:33:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦，好啊  - 我就知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Oh, fine. - I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.75,0:34:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我告诉你为什么吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Would you like me to tell you why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.57,0:34:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我不想你告诉我为什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, I wouldn't like you to tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.76,0:34:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我想澄清，如果你不介意的话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to make it clear anyway, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们非得听这个吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do we have to listen to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.10,0:34:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人有话要说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The man wants to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.59,0:34:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.30,0:34:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生一直独自对抗我们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This gentleman has been standing alone against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他并没有说那孩子无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He doesn't say the boy is not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.18,0:34:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是无法确定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He just isn't sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.21,0:34:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要独自对抗别人的嘲讽并不容易\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not easy to stand alone against the ridicule of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.18,0:34:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他赌了一把 争取支持。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So he gambled for support
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.89,0:34:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持了他。我尊重他的动机。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and I gave it to him. I respect his motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个受审的孩子或许有罪，但是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy on trial is probably guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.82,0:34:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想多听听\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but I want to hear more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.79,0:34:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的票数是十比二\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right now the vote is ten to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.62,0:34:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在讲话! 你没有权利离开这房间！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm talking! You have no right to leave this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.71,0:34:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会听你的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.16,0:34:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝不会的。我们坐下吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He never will. Let's sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.07,0:34:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以继续了吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.93,0:34:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 我们应该休息一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I think we ought to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.20,0:34:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道，有人在里面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, one man's inside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.21,0:34:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该等他\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and I think we ought to wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们真的被困在这里了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Looks like we're really hung up here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.65,0:34:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人做的事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That thing with the old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.75,0:35:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料不到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}that was pretty unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.05,0:35:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我能想出办法打破局面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wish I could figure out some way we could break it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.26,0:35:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？在广告界...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, in advertising...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.40,0:35:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我在代理公司工作吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I told you I worked in an agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.95,0:35:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些怪人在那里工作\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Some pretty strange people work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.60,0:35:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上不奇怪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, not strange, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.12,0:35:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只是他们表达自己的方式很独特\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I guess it's just they have peculiar ways of expressing themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.30,0:35:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，我猜在你那一行也一样吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I suppose it's the same in your business too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.47,0:35:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做什么的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.97,0:35:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个钟表匠\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm a watchmaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.34,0:35:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想象中 世上最出色的钟表匠都来自欧洲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I imagine the finest watchmakers in the world come from Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.58,0:35:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，在代理公司 要是遇到这种情形\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyway, in an agency, when we reach a point like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.72,0:35:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在跟他说，在广告代理中\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm telling him, in an ad agency
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.50,0:35:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是会议中 遇到这种情形\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}when a point like this is reached in a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.42,0:35:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有个人准备了一个点子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}there's always some character ready with an idea, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.81,0:35:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真笑死我了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.02,0:35:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是世上最怪异的事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's the weirdest thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.25,0:35:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说出自己的主意时 有时候用的短语\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the way they sometimes precede their idea with a phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.03,0:35:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像，有个账务主任站起来说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Like, some account exec will get up and he'll say:
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.01,0:35:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"好了，我有一个点子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"OK, here's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.03,0:35:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...把它挂到旗杆上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's...run it up the flagpole
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.39,0:35:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看有没有人欢迎它"\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and see if anyone salutes it."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.84,0:35:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然挺蠢的  但很好笑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, it's idiotic, but it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.87,0:36:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.94,0:36:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚太激动了一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}got a little excited back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.45,0:36:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无意惹人不快\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I...didn't mean to get nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好你不是那种会被情绪影响的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Glad you're not one of those who lets these emotional appeals influence him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.17,0:36:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那个电扇怎么回事，就是没法启动。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know what's the matter with that fan. Can seem to get it start.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.18,0:36:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是推销员吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are you a salesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.38,0:36:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个建筑师\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm an architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.09,0:36:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道软性推销是什么吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know what the soft sell is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.16,0:36:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有这个技能，相信我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, you've got it, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.80,0:36:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的技能不一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've got a different technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.30,0:37:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笑，喝酒，开玩笑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Laughs, drinks, jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.31,0:37:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小手段。你懂吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}tricks. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.27,0:37:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.97,0:37:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击中他们的生活，那是我的座右铭\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hit 'em where they live , that's my motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.58,0:37:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年我卖橘子果酱赚了两万七\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I made 27 grand last year sellin' marmalade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.72,0:37:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 毕竟那是橘子果酱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, you know, considerin' marmalade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.99,0:37:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从这里能得到什么？刺激吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you gettin' out of this? Kicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.49,0:37:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有人撞过你的头...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Or did somebody bump you on the head once
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.31,0:37:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有恢复过来？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and you haven't gotten over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.33,0:37:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.21,0:37:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗，你们这些好人都一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, you do-gooders are all alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.87,0:37:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是把自己的快乐建立在别人的痛苦上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're always blowin' your stacks over some guy that fanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.54,0:37:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你浪费我们的时间做什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But what are you wastin' our time for?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.31,0:37:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何不捐五块钱出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why don't you donate five dollars to the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.67,0:37:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许能让你感觉好些\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe it'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.55,0:37:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子有罪，哥们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This kid is guilty, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.92,0:37:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是和尚头上的虱子-明摆着\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's as plain as the nose on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.29,0:37:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们干吗不停止浪费大家的时间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So why don't we stop wastin' our time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.86,0:37:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续下去大家的喉咙都疼了，知道吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're gonna all get sore throats if we keep it up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.66,0:38:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么区别？在这里，或看球赛都会疼。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What difference does it make if you get it here or at the ball game?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.60,0:38:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有区别，哥们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No difference, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.97,0:38:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有区别\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No difference at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.94,0:38:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮人不错，对吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nice bunch of guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.62,0:38:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟其他人都一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They're about the same as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.05,0:38:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，真是凶恶的一天\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, what a murderous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.56,0:38:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我们还会很久吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you think we'll be much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.06,0:38:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.96,0:38:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他绝对有罪。全世界没有一个人会怀疑。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's guilty for sure. Not a doubt in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早该...我们早该结束了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We should've... We should've been done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.13,0:38:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不介意，你知道。比上班强。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I don't mind, you know. Beats workin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.04,0:38:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为他无罪，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You think he's not guilty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.55,0:38:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。有可能。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.88,0:38:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认识你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I don't know you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.86,0:38:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我打赌 你一生从未如此错过\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but I'm bettin' you've never been wronger in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.82,0:38:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在浪费你的时间，你得收拾这摊子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're wastin' your time. You ought to wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.35,0:39:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设受审的人是你呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposing you were the one who was on trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.29,0:39:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不习惯假设，我只是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I'm not used to supposin'. I'm just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个打工的，我老板负责假设，但是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}workin' man. My boss does the supposin'. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.63,0:39:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会试试的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll try one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.33,0:39:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设你真的说服了我们全体，而...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Supposin' you talk us all out of this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.67,0:39:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真的刀杀了他父亲呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the kid really did knife his father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.25,0:39:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.68,0:39:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了，蓝眼哥\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sorry, blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.42,0:39:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 能在哪？  - 好了，大家就坐吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Well, where else? - OK, fellas. Let's take our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.66,0:39:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们得在这里吃晚餐\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Looks like we'll be here for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.89,0:39:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们来办正事。谁想开头？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, now let's get down to business. Who wants to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.56,0:39:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我来  - 好，你请说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- I will. - OK, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你，那边的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You, down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.62,0:39:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在楼下的老头\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man who lived downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.92,0:39:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他听到那孩子大叫“我要杀了你”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}says he heard the kid yell "I'm gonna kill ya."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒后，他听到人体倒在地板上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A second later, he heard the body hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.91,0:39:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑到门口，看到那孩子跑下楼，出了房子。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now he ran to the door and saw the kid runing down the stairs out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.99,0:39:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你怎么想？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.28,0:39:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道 那老人听男孩的声音能有多清楚\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I wonder how clearly the old man heard the boy's voice
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.98,0:40:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔着天花板\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}through the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.02,0:40:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有通过天花板听，窗户开着。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He didn't hear through the celling. The window was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.93,0:40:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楼上那扇也是。那晚很热，记得吗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So was the one upstairs. It was a hot night. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.15,0:40:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是另一个公寓房间。辨认声音没那么容易\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was another apartment. It's not easy to identify a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.85,0:40:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是喊声\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}espacilly a shouting voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.08,0:40:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在庭上辨认出来了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He identified it in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.42,0:40:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错。别忘了住在对街的女士\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's right. And don't forget the lady across the street
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.47,0:40:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就在打开的窗户那 看到那孩子刺死他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She looked right in the open window and saw the boy stabbed his farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.13,0:40:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思，对你来说还不够吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know what I mean, isn't that enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.77,0:40:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不够\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.83,0:40:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，这家伙怎能这样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy,  this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.35,0:40:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直是对牛弹琴\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's like talkin' into a dead phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.25,0:40:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她透过行驶的电车车窗看到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She said she saw it through the windows of a moving el train.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.72,0:40:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车一共有六节车厢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There were six cars on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.36,0:40:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她透过最后两节车厢看到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She saw it through the last two.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.45,0:40:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她记得最小的细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She remembered the most insignificant details.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.31,0:40:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不出你如何能反驳这一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't see how you can argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.58,0:40:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有谁知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Has anybody here any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车要花多少时间...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}how long it would take an el...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.26,0:40:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是游戏\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.13,0:40:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.23,0:40:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.34,0:40:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好了，听着，他...  - 他简直是神经！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}-All right, listen, he...  -The absolute nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.77,0:41:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，算了。这没什么。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Forget it. It's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.57,0:41:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是游戏？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This isn't a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.14,0:41:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 冷静点  - 他以为他是什么东西?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Calm down. - Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.81,0:41:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Forget it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.25,0:41:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有谁知道 一辆电车要花多少时间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Has anybody any idea how long it takes an el train
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.69,0:41:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以中等速度通过某一定点吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}at medium speed to pass a given point?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.69,0:41:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那有什么意义？ - 多久？猜一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}-What is that to do? -How long? Take a guess
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.83,0:41:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我一点概念都没有  - 你觉得呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- I wouldn't have any idea. - What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.06,0:41:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。或许10或12秒吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. Ten, twelve seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.93,0:41:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这猜测很不错。还有人吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A pretty good guess. Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.76,0:41:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得正确\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sounds right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.92,0:41:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，猜这个干嘛？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the guessing game for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.56,0:41:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你说呢?  - 10秒钟差不多\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What do you say? - Ten seconds is about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.63,0:41:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，就说10秒钟。你想表达什么呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. Say 10 seconds. What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.74,0:41:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有六节车厢的电车要花10秒钟通过一个定点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It takes a six-car el train ten seconds to pass a given point.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.71,0:41:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，我们说那一点就是凶案房间那扇开着的窗户。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now let's say the given point is the open window of the room where the killing took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.04,0:41:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你伸手出去几乎可以摸到铁轨，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can reach out and almost touch the el tracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.38,0:41:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要问你们这个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.84,0:41:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们之中有人曾住在铁轨旁边吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Has anyone here ever lived near the el tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.35,0:41:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚油漆完一间可以俯视电车线的公寓。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just finished painting an apartment that overlooked an el line.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.23,0:41:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那里待了三天。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was there for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.48,0:41:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是什么样的？  - 你是什么意思?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What was it like? - What you means?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.52,0:41:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很吵？  - 哦，伙计！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Noisy? - Oh, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.91,0:41:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没关系，我们都头昏眼花。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No matter. We were punchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.97,0:41:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经住在电车线附近\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I lived in an apartment near the el line once.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.36,0:41:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户开着的时候\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When the window's open,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:41:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车噪音大到难以忍受\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the train noise is almost unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.57,0:42:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎连心里的想法都听不见。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can hardly hear yourself think.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.46,0:42:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，你听不见自己想什么。你讲重点好吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, you can't hear yourself think. Will you get to the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.30,0:42:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的，等一分钟\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I will. Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.94,0:42:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿出两个证词，试试拼在一起。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, let's take two pieces of testimony and try to put them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.61,0:42:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先：住在楼下公寓的老人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}First: The old man in the apartment downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.75,0:42:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 听到那孩子说“我要杀了你”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He says he heard the boy say "I'm gonna kill you"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.77,0:42:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间后他听到人体摔倒在地\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and a split second later heard a body hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.22,0:42:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒钟后，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}one second later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.69,0:42:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对  - 第二点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Right. - Second...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.46,0:42:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对街那女人肯定地发誓说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The woman across the street swore positively
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.23,0:42:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从窗户往外看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}she looked out of the window
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.03,0:42:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透过最后两节车厢看到凶杀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and saw the killing through the last two cars of a passing el train
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.53,0:42:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧，最后两节车厢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right? the last two cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.86,0:42:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你想跟我们说什么？  - 等一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What are you givin' us here? - Now, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.23,0:42:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都同意电车得花十秒钟\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We've agreed that it takes ten seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.53,0:42:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能通过某一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}for a train to pass a given point.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.51,0:42:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那女人是透过最后两节车厢看到凶杀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Since the woman saw the killing through the last two cars
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.91,0:42:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以推测出身体倒地时...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}we can assume that the body hit the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.60,0:42:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车正好经过。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}just as the train went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.15,0:42:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此，电车隆隆地经过老人窗口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Therefore, the train had been roaring by the old man's window
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整十秒后死者倒在地上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}a full ten seconds before the body hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.16,0:42:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人，根据他自己的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man，acording to his own testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.39,0:42:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我要杀了你”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"I'm gonna kill you"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.40,0:43:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒后 人体跌在地板上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}body hitting the floor a second later
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.53,0:43:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 他听到那孩子说这话的时候\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}would have had to hear the boy made his statment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.17,0:43:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车正隆隆经过他鼻子底下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}with the el roaring past his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.13,0:43:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能听得到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not possible he heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.63,0:43:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用喊的，他当然听到了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's it. He yelled. Of course he heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.01,0:43:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为他能听到？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you think he could have heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.83,0:43:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他是最高声调大叫，我觉得够了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said he yelled at the top of his voice. That's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.17,0:43:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他听到什么，他也不可能辨认声音。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Even he heared something. He still couldn't have identified the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.70,0:43:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车正轰隆隆经过。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}with the el roaring by.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.80,0:43:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说几秒钟内的事情。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're talking about a matter of seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.42,0:43:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人可以那么准确\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody can be that accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.77,0:43:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为能送那孩子上电椅的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well I think testimony that could put a boy into the electric chair
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.41,0:43:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须那么准确才行\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}should be that accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.15,0:43:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他听不出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think he could have heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.88,0:43:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他听不出来，我是说那么吵\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe he didn't, I mean with all that el noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.56,0:43:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人在说什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you people talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.56,0:43:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有站得住的理由，他可能听不到。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It stands to reason he couldn't have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.72,0:43:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么说谎？对他有什么好处？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why should he lie? What's he got to gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.13,0:43:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关注，也许是。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Attention, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.93,0:43:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不断提出高明的说法。你怎么不把它们卖给报社？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You keep comin' in with bright sayings. Why don't you send 'em to a paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.27,0:43:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们付三块钱一条!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They pay $3 a piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.22,0:43:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么那样对他说话?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you talkin' to him like that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.21,0:43:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子跟老人说话的人...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A guy who talks like that to an old man
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.69,0:43:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该要受到谴责，你知道吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}really oughta get stepped on, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.14,0:43:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该多尊重别人，先生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You oughta have more respect, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.78,0:43:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再那样子跟他说话。。。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You say stuff like that to him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.74,0:43:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你好看。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm gonna lay you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.46,0:44:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你继续。想说什么就说。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You go ahead. You say anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.26,0:44:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得那老人可能说谎呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why do you think the old man might lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.40,0:44:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在法庭上看他看了很久\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was just that I looked at him for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.54,0:44:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的外套接缝开线了，在肩膀下面。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The seam of his jacket was split, under the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.87,0:44:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们注意到了吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Did you notice that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.31,0:44:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 那样子上法庭\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, to come into court like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.01,0:44:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个很老的人 穿着破外套\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was a very old man in a torn jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.92,0:44:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他走上站台的非常慢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And he walked very slowly to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.49,0:44:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拖着左脚\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was dragging his left leg
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却努力地掩饰它\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and trying to hide it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.63,0:44:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他觉得丢人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}because he was ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.43,0:44:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我比这里的人都了解这个人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think I know this man better than anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.63,0:44:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个安静，胆怯，不起眼的老头子...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is a quiet, frightened, insignificant old man who...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.20,0:44:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...他一辈子无所成。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}who has been nothing all his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.88,0:44:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没人重视他\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who has never had recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字也没有上过报\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}or his name in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.98,0:45:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人认识他。没人征询他的话。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody knows him. Nobody quotes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.42,0:45:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,75年来没有人征询过他的意见。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody seeks his advice after 75 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.16,0:45:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们，生无意义是一件非常悲哀的事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Gentlemen, that's a very sad thing-to mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.83,0:45:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的人需要被征询\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A man like this needs to be quoted,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.50,0:45:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人倾听\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to be listened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.52,0:45:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被征询到一次  对他来说很重要。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}To be quoted just once-very important to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.04,0:45:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他退回幕后很难\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It would be so hard for him to recede into the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不，等一下。  - 一旦有机会...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- No, wait a minute. - Whenever get a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.32,0:45:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是告诉我们 他说谎只是为了重要一回？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are you tellin' us he'd lie just so he could be important once?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.08,0:45:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。他是真的说谎。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. He wouldn't really lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.11,0:45:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也许让自己相信他真的听到那些话。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But perhaps he made himself believe he heard those words
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.43,0:45:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还认出了那男孩的脸\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and recognised the boy's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.99,0:45:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有史以来我听过最玄妙的事情了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's the most fantastic story I ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.42,0:45:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么编得出这种事？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How can you make up a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.87,0:45:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事你懂个啥？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.33,0:45:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 噢，谁想吃喉糖？  - 不了，谢谢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, does anybody want a cough drop? -No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.58,0:45:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一颗。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.74,0:45:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢说什么就说。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You say what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.83,0:46:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是看不出怎么会有人认为他无罪。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I still don't see how anybody can think he's not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.45,0:46:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事我想讨论一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's something else I'd like to talk about for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.81,0:46:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.71,0:46:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们证明了那老人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We've proved the old man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.67,0:46:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到那孩子说“我要杀了你”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}couldn't have heard the boy say "I'm gonna kill you."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.05,0:46:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但，假设...  - 你根本没有证明，你说什么呢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- but, suppose...  -You didn't prove it at all! What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.28,0:46:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，假设他真的听到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wait. Supposing he really did hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.69,0:46:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话，我们大家说过多少次了？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This phrase, how many times have all of us used it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.12,0:46:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许好几千次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Probably thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.69,0:46:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“为这事我要杀了你，亲爱的”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"I could kill you for that, darling."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.79,0:46:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“少年，再干一次，我就杀了你。”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"Junior, you do that once morn and I'll kill you."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.62,0:46:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“进去，洛基...”\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"Get in there, Rocky..."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.71,0:46:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们天天说。不代表我们真的要杀谁。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We say it everyday. It doesn't mean we're really gonna kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.16,0:46:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我们说什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What're you trying to give us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.52,0:46:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句“我要杀了你”。那孩子用最高嗓子喊出来的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The phrase was 'I'm gonna kill you'. The kid yelled it at the top of his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.64,0:46:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉我他不是这个意思。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't tell me he didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.82,0:46:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人像他那样说这句话，都是认真的！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anybody says a thing like the way he says, they mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.37,0:46:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊，我可不知道了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Gee, now I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.14,0:46:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得几个星期前我和银行的一个工作伙伴争吵。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I remember I was arguing with the guy I work next to at the bank a few weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.98,0:46:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骂我是白痴  于是我对他大喊\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He called me an idiot, so I yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.55,0:46:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，这家伙要你们相信不实之事！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh listen, this guy is trying to make you believe what isn't so!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.72,0:46:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子说要杀了他 而且真的杀了他!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid said he'd kill him and he did kill he!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.72,0:46:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来问你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.83,0:46:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的认为那孩子喊出这种事...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you really think the boy'd shout out a thing like that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.83,0:46:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让所有邻居都听见吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}so the whole neighbourhood could hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.56,0:46:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不这么看，他可聪明得多\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think so. He's much too bright for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.56,0:46:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明？他只是个普通的愚昧粗人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Bright? He's a common, ignorant slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.38,0:46:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至连英语都不说好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He don't even speak good English.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.43,0:47:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至连英语都 {\u1}说不好{\r}\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He doesn't even speak good English.{\fn\fs\fn\fs\u0\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.60,0:47:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Mr.Foreman,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.06,0:47:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要改投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to change my vote to not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.14,0:47:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你什么？  - 你听到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- You what? - You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.18,0:47:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.48,0:47:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我确定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.98,0:47:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,票数九比三有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The vote is nine to three in favour of guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.58,0:47:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好么，可这还不是最后的结论，嗯？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, if this isn't the livin' end! huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.02,0:47:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么依据？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you basin' it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙编的故事?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Stories this guy made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.79,0:47:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该给那些怪异的侦探杂志写稿\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You oughta write for one of those kooky detective magazines,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.09,0:47:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚大钱\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}just make a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.03,0:47:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到那声大喊，那孩子自己的律师都知道他没有机会\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}For cryin' out loud, the kid's own lawyer knew he didn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.77,0:47:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始，他的律师就知道，你能看得出来。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right from the beginning, his own lawyer knew, and you could see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.27,0:47:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，伙计，我告诉你。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, oh boy, I'm telling ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.87,0:47:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里这家伙，他真行。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This guy here is really somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.81,0:47:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子有个律师，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid had a lawyer, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.49,0:47:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他代表他出庭，不是你。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He presented his case, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.22,0:47:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么你要说这么多？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How come you say so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.62,0:47:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律师不是一贯正确，你知道的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Lawyers aren't infallible, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔的摩迷，拜托。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Baltimore，please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.62,0:47:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是法庭指派的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was court-appointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.33,0:47:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么意义？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.57,0:47:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能意味着很多事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well it can mean a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.77,0:47:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能意味着他不想要这案子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It can mean that he didn't want the case
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.82,0:47:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者他不爽被指派\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}or he resented being appointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.88,0:48:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这类案子对他没好处\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's the kind of case brings him nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.25,0:48:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱，没名声，甚至没什么机会赢。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}no money, no glory, not even much chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.63,0:48:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对年轻律师来说，那不是很有前途的形势。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's not a very promising situation for a young lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.77,0:48:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必须真的信任他的当事人 才能打好案子。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He'd really have to believe in his client to put up any kind of a good case.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.66,0:48:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一分钟前你已经指出，他显然没有。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You pointed out a minute ago, obviously he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.74,0:48:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当然没有。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Of course he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.78,0:48:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能做到呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who the heck could?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.08,0:48:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许某人的妈妈或什么人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Except maybe some guy's mother or somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.01,0:48:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看。你们不看看时间么？得了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, look. Will you look at the time? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.32,0:48:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对不起  我做了一些笔记 - 笔记？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Pardon me. I have made some notes here... - Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.42,0:48:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一些话  想要告诉你们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and I would like, please, to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.32,0:48:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直非常仔细地在听\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have been listening very carefully and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.89,0:48:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说，这人似乎提出了一些很好的观点。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}it seems to me that this man has some very good points to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.06,0:48:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从审讯中呈现的东西看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}From what was presented at the trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.47,0:48:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子看起来有罪 表面上。但是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the boy looks guilty, on the surface. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.24,0:48:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 也许我们深入去...  - 少来了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- maybe if we go deeper... - Come on, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.84,0:48:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个问题 我想问问\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There is a question I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.24,0:48:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们假设那孩子真的实施了谋杀。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let us assume that the boy really did commit the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.68,0:48:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案发的时间是12点10分\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, this happened at 10 minutes after 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.12,0:48:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是怎么被警方逮捕的呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, how was he caught by the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.65,0:49:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回家了，在...三点左右\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He came back home... at three o'clock or so
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.19,0:49:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被两名警官逮捕 在他房子的走廊里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and he was captured by two detectives in the hallway of his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.99,0:49:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，我的问题是\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, my question is:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.96,0:49:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他真的杀了他的父亲...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If he really had killed his father
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.66,0:49:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他要在三个小时后回家？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}why would he come back home three hours later?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.07,0:49:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他不怕会被逮到吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wouldn't he be afraid of being caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.00,0:49:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回家拿刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He came home to get his knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.51,0:49:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀留在别人胸口上不好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not nice to leave knives in people's chests.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.34,0:49:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，特别是亲戚的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, especially relatives'.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.24,0:49:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这没什么好笑的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't see anything funny about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.55,0:49:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男孩知道会有人指认出 那是他刚买的刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy knew the knife could be identified is the one he just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.19,0:49:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得赶在警察前面拿走它\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He had to get it before the police did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.39,0:49:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果他知道刀会被认出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If he knew the knife could be identified,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.70,0:49:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么一开始要把它留在现场？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}why did he leave it there in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.49,0:49:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们可以假设 那男孩在慌张中跑了出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I think we can assume the boy ran out in a state of panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.38,0:49:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚杀了自己的父亲。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}after having just killed his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.73,0:49:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最后冷静下来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He finally calmed down
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.25,0:49:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意识到他把刀留在那儿了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and realised he'd left his knife there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.17,0:49:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个，就得看你对慌张的定义了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This, then, depends on your definition of panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.10,0:49:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必须非常地冷静\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He would have had to be calm enough
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.54,0:49:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会把刀上的所有指纹擦掉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to wipe off any fingerprints left on the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.97,0:49:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慌张是什么时候开始的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, where did this panic start
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.62,0:49:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是什么时候结束的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and where did it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.15,0:50:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你投了有罪一票  你是哪一边的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You voted guilty. What side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.08,0:50:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信 我不必效忠于一边或另一边\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't believe I have to be loyal to one side or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.23,0:50:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仅仅是提出问题\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm simply asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.12,0:50:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的已经超出了我的理解范围  但是\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is just off the top of my head but...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.42,0:50:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是那男孩 我刺杀了人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If I was the boy, I'd done the stabbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.45,0:50:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会冒险回去拿刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd take a chance and go back for the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.93,0:50:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打赌 他琢磨没有人看到他跑出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll bet he figured nobody'd seen him running out
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.52,0:50:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体要到隔天才会被发现\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and the body wouldn't be discovered till the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.37,0:50:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 那时是半夜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}After all, it was the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.17,0:50:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打赌他琢磨第二天才会被发现\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I bet he figured it'd be found the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.49,0:50:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起。那就是我的重点。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pardon. This is my whole point.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.91,0:50:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对街那女人作证说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The woman across the street testified that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.42,0:50:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看见凶杀之后的时刻\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the moment after she saw the killing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.62,0:50:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是在电车经过之后的时刻\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}that is a moment after the train went by
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.18,0:50:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她大叫，然后去打电话报警。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}she screamed, and then went to telephone the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.52,0:50:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子当然一定听到了尖叫声。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, the boy certainly must have heard the scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.02,0:50:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他知道有人看到了什么。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So he knew that somebody saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.59,0:50:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得他不会回去。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just don't think that he would have gone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.34,0:50:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两件事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.28,0:50:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一：在慌乱中，他也许没听到尖叫声。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One: in the state of panic he may not have heard the scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.40,0:50:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能声音不是很大。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Perhaps it wasn't very loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.96,0:50:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二：即使他听到，他也许没有和自己的行为联系起来。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Two: If he did hear it, he may not have connected it with his own acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.53,0:50:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住，他住的社区里尖叫声是常事。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Remember, he lived in a neighbourhood where screams were commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.50,0:50:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的答案。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.82,0:50:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.11,0:51:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这男孩的确杀了他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe the boy did kill his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.16,0:51:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确没听见叫声\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Didn't hear the scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.41,0:51:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确慌张地冲出去，的确...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}did run out in a panic, did...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.35,0:51:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三小时后冷静下来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}calmed down 3 hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.38,0:51:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去拿刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and came back for the knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.56,0:51:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒着被警察抓住的风险\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}risking being caught by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.73,0:51:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这些事都发生了，但也许不是\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe those things happened, but maybe they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.75,0:51:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有足够多的疑点 让我们怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think there's enough doubt we can wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.46,0:51:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶杀时他到底在不在那里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}if he was there at all at the time of the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.96,0:51:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑点是什么意思？你在说什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean doubt? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.55,0:51:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人没有看见他跑出房子吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Didn't the old man see him running out of the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.43,0:51:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在扭曲事实 我跟你们说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's twisting the facts. I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.63,0:51:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人看没看见那孩子在12:10跑出房子？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Did or didn't the old man see the kid running out of the house at 12.10?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.20,0:51:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看到了还是没有？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, did or didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.97,0:51:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他看到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He says he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.17,0:51:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他看到了？伙计，你怎么能这样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Says he did? Boy, how do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.48,0:51:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证人会犯错的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Witnesses can make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.81,0:51:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，你想当然的时候！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure, when you want them to!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.45,0:51:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或他想当然的时候。你知道我的意思。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Or when he wants them to! You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.51,0:51:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音放低点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Keep the yelling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.49,0:51:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你老是这么说。或许我们需要大声点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, you keep saying that. Maybe we need a little yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.25,0:51:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙越来越过份了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}These guys keep going off every which way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.22,0:51:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他听见尖叫吗？他没有听见吗？有什么分别?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Did hear the scream, didn't hear it-what difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.75,0:51:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人只讨论那些小细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're talking about only little details
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.79,0:51:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却忘了重要的事，我意思是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and forgetting the important stuff. I mean all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.19,0:51:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我提议再投一次票  - 我正在说话!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- I call for another vote. - I'm talking here!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.39,0:51:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求再投一次票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Another vote called for.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.57,0:51:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们就坐吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now let's take our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.93,0:52:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过无端浪费这么多时间。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I never saw so much time spent on nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.64,0:52:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过花点时间。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It only takes a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.50,0:52:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我想最快的办法 是看看谁投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, I guess the fastest way is to find out who's voting not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.14,0:52:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投无罪票的 请举手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All those voting not guilty, please raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.85,0:52:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一样，一、二、三票无罪，九票有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Still the same. One, two, three not guilty. Nine guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.65,0:52:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在有何进展？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So now where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.15,0:52:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以喋喋不休到下周二\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can yakety-yak till next Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.12,0:52:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们有什么好处？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where's it getting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.92,0:52:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起。我投无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pardon. I vote not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.36,0:52:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.71,0:52:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我们全都疯了是怎么的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, we're all goin' crazy in here or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.23,0:52:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子有罪。你们为什么不听听事实？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid is guilty. Why don't you listen to the facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.17,0:52:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们，好吗？这要成为笑话了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Tell them, will ya? This is gettin' to be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.44,0:52:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,票数是八比四有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The vote is eight to four in favour of guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.84,0:52:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.67,0:52:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持弱势团体周 还是什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Love Your Underprivileged Brother Week or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.88,0:52:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你告诉我 你为什么改了投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I want you to tell me why you changed your vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.19,0:52:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，告诉我理由\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, now give me reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.68,0:52:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不必为我的决定 跟你辩护\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't have to defend my decision to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.46,0:52:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里有合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There is a reasonable doubt in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.42,0:52:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么合理怀疑？除了说辞什么也没有。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Reasonable doubt? There's nothing but words.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.30,0:52:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，看看这个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.52,0:52:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚认定无罪的那孩子 被看见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The kid you just decided isn't guilty was seen
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.97,0:53:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个捅了他父亲!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}ramming this into his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.53,0:53:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西如何？合理怀疑先生？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about this, Mr.Reasonable Doubt?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.57,0:53:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是凶刀。你不记得吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's not the knife, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.63,0:53:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，精彩啊!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.70,0:53:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你们 这太疯狂了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm tellin' you, this is the craziest.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.97,0:53:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我们应该相信什么?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, what are we supposed to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.98,0:53:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们削尖脑袋 凭空编出许多故事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean you shap your head. You're pullin' stories out of thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.21,0:53:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的人，要是在拳击场看过邓普西跟佛波对打\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A guy like this, if he's sittin' ringside at the Dempsey-Firpo fight
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.04,0:53:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就会告诉你们...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he'd be trying to tell you that...
