Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.77,0:53:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 等一下  - 他说了跑，至少我觉得他说了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Hold on a second. - He said he ran. At least I think he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.01,0:53:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得他怎么说的，但我看不出他能跑到门口。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't remember, but I don't see how he could have run.
