Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.08,0:53:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你什么都记得，却不记得那个？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I thought you remember everything, don't you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.45,0:54:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不记得。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.54,0:54:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主席先生，我想看看那栋公寓的配置图。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Foreman, I'd like to see a diagram of the apartment.
