Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.58,0:54:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他说20秒  - 他说15\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- He said 20. - He said 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.15,0:54:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了20秒. 你干吗要歪曲？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said 20 seconds. What are you tryin' to distort?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.64,0:54:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说15\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said 15.
