Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.49,0:54:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说15. 对此他非常肯定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said 15. He was positive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.95,0:54:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个老人!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was an old man!
