Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.32,0:54:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不出你想证明什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't see what you're going to prove here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.12,0:54:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人说了他看到那男孩跑出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The man said he saw the boy running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来看看细节是否支持他\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's see if the details bear him out.
