Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.25,0:54:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他就听到楼上的脚步声跑到前门。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he said he heard footsteps upstairs, running to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.54,0:55:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到楼上的门打开，脚步声开始下楼\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Heard the upstairs door open, the footsteps start down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他尽快来到自己的门口 发誓说不超过15秒\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He said he got to his own door as fast, he swore couldn't more than 15 seconds.
