Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.78,0:55:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛不停止这些聪明的评论？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why don't you stop making smart remarks all the time?
