Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.28,0:55:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里一天赚3块钱 你什么都得听听\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}for your three dollars a day you have to listen to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.10,0:55:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，这是凶杀发生的公寓。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Alright, here's the apartment where the killing tookplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.00,0:55:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人的公寓就在楼下，完全一样。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man's apartment was directly beneath and exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.86,0:55:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是电车轨，卧室，客厅\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here are the el tracks, the bedroom, living room,
