Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.15,0:55:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好及时看见那孩子跑下楼\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}just in time to see the boy running down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.98,0:55:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止我没错吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Am I right so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.37,0:55:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这个说法 19遍了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's the story, for the 19th time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.77,0:55:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体倒地后的15秒内。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}15 seconds after the body hit the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.34,0:55:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 正确  - 现在 我们看看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Correct. - Now, let's see. It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.44,0:55:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从床到门12尺。走廊有43尺\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's 12 feet from the bed to the door. The hall is 43 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.55,0:55:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得走上12尺 打开卧室门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He would have had to walk 12 feet, open the bedroom door
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.82,0:55:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过43尺的走廊 打开前门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}walk 43 feet down and open the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.32,0:56:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在15秒内\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}all in 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.48,0:56:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们觉得他办得到吗?  - 当然，他能做到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Could he have done it? - Sure. He cound have done it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.76,0:56:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只能很慢地走路。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He can walk only very slowly.
