Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.60,0:56:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对一个老人，还中过风，的确是很长的路。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}For an old man who had a stroke, it is a long walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你在做什么?  - 我打算试一下，看他要走多久。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What are you doin'? - I'm gonna try it. See how he took.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.84,0:56:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思，你要试一下？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean you wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.33,0:56:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的律师为什么在法庭上不提出来？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why didn't his lawyer bring it up himself on the court?
