Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.24,0:56:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为那人是白痴什么的吗？这是显然的事。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You think the man is an idiot or something? It's an obvious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.24,0:56:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想到了吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.19,0:56:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是聪明人，别管我想没想到。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're a so smart guy don't matter what I thought of.
