Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.03,0:56:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负和纠缠一个无助的老人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}bullying and badgering a helpless old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.62,0:56:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道在陪审团面前不好看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know that doesn't sit well with a jury.
