Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.56,0:56:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我一直在问的问题。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's what I've been asking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.73,0:56:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那张椅子拿给我，行吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pass me that chair, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.43,0:56:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两把椅子是那老人的床\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Those two chairs are the old man's bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.96,0:56:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚在房间步测了十二尺\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I just paced off 12 feet across the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.56,0:56:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是卧室门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is the bedroom door.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.85,0:56:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯了，你不能那样子重建现场\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's crazy. You can't re-create a thing like that.
