Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.54,0:56:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有这时间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We can spare that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.35,0:57:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了。闭上嘴。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on. Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.69,0:57:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好 好，牛人。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. OK, OK, killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.23,0:57:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就站在那里当前门好吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Will you stand right there and mark the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.56,0:57:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它上了门链，根据证词，记得吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was chain-locked, acoding to the testmony, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.96,0:57:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谁的手表有秒针?  - 我的有\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Who's got a watch with a second hand? - I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.17,0:57:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跺脚我就开始。就算是人倒地的声音。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You wanna me to start, stamp your foot. That'll be the body falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.48,0:57:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从那时给我计时\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can time me from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.74,0:57:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要干吗？比划游戏？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are we gonna do, play charades?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.74,0:57:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在等什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.54,0:57:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得等到秒针指到60\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I wanna wait till the second hand reaches 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.61,0:57:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，得了吧!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.65,0:57:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，快一点。他能走得比你快两倍\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, speed it up. He can walk twice as fast as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.13,0:57:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我比现在快一点，我会的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If you want me to walk faster than that, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.48,0:58:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 锁。门。停。  - 好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Lock. Door. Stop. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.85,0:58:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间是多少？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.35,0:58:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好41秒\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Exactly...41 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.62,0:58:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我认为真正发生的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is what I think happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.65,0:58:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几小时前，那老人听到那男孩和他父亲的争吵声。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man heard the fight between the boy and his farther a few hours earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.69,0:58:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来他躺在床上，听到男孩公寓有人倒在地板上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When he's in bed, he heard the body hit the floor of the boy's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.59,0:58:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见对街那女人的尖叫\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}heard the woman scream from across the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.56,0:58:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快来到他的前门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}got to his front door as fast as he could
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.20,0:58:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到有人在跑下楼，他假设是那孩子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}heard somebody running down stairs and assumed it was the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.67,0:58:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那是有可能的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.85,0:58:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Assumed?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.30,0:58:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟 我的生活中见过各式各样的骗局\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Brother, I've seen all kinds of dishonesty in my day,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.50,0:58:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这场小表演拔得头筹了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but this little display takes the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.41,0:58:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来到这里 心里充满对贫民窟孩子和非正义的感慨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You all come in here with your hearts bleedin' about slum kids and injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.38,0:58:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听了些童话故事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You listen to some fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.44,0:58:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然间，你开始说服了这些老女人。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Suddenly you start getting through to these old ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.82,0:58:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是骗不过我的。我受够了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're not getting through to me. I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.79,0:58:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是怎么了？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the matter with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.79,0:58:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都知道他有罪！他应该被烧死！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You all know he's guilty! He's got to burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.32,0:58:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要让他逃脱我们的手心了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're letting him slip through our fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.36,0:58:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃脱我们的手心，你是他的行刑人吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Slip through our fingers? Are you his executioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.82,0:58:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是其中之一。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.40,0:59:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你想按下开关\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Perhaps you'd like to pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.71,0:59:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这孩子，你可以押注我会的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}For this kid, you bet I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.74,0:59:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你感到遗憾\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.83,0:59:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要按下开关心里得是什么感觉！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What it must feel like to wanna pull the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.78,0:59:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你走进这房间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ever since you walked in,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.08,0:59:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像是一个自封的公众复仇者\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}you've acted like a self-appointed public avenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.85,0:59:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看到这男孩去死，只因为你个人想\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You want to see this boy die because you personally want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.08,0:59:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}not because of the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.00,0:59:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个虐待狂\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're a sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.82,0:59:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！我要杀了他！我要杀了他！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let me go! I'll kill him! I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.42,0:59:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思不是真的要杀我，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You don't really mean you'll kill me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.07,0:59:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了，先生们？我听到吵闹声\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anything wrong, gentlemen? I heard some noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.68,0:59:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，什么事也没有。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, everything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.87,0:59:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是...你知道，友好的小争执。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're just...You know, friendly little argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.90,0:59:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经看过配置图了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, we're through with that diagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.73,0:59:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拿走它。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can take it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.08,0:59:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.45,0:59:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在看什么?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.07,1:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想，得有人重新起个头。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I suppose somebody has to start off again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.07,1:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I beg pardon...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.14,1:00:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“请原谅。” 你怎么那么有礼貌？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}"I beg pardon." What are you so polite about?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.31,1:00:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你没礼貌的原因一样。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}For the same reason you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.25,1:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样被养大的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's the way I was brought up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.39,1:00:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种争吵。这不是我们来这里的原因。吵架。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This fighting. That's not why we are here, to fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.47,1:00:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们背负着责任\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We have a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.06,1:00:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个，我一直觉得，是民主社会的一项非凡之处\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This, I have always thought, is a remarkable thing about democracy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.70,1:00:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是，我们...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That we are...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.34,1:00:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个单词是什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What is the word?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.14,1:00:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，被通知\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Notified.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.57,1:00:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到信件通知，来这里...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That we are notified by mail to come down to this place
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.35,1:00:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来决定一个人有罪还是无辜，这人...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to decide on the guilt or innocence of a man we...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.47,1:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...我们从没听说过的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}we have never heard of before.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.18,1:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有什么好处或是损失\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We have nothing to gain or lose
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.80,1:00:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是裁决\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}by...by our verdict.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.62,1:01:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们强大的原因之一\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is one of the reasons why we are strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不应该把它变成私人恩怨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We should not make it a... personal thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.10,1:01:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.40,1:01:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有人有主意  我也许有个好玩的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If nobody else has an idea, I might have a cutie here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.60,1:01:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们考虑很多了，现在让我们把它扔到垃圾场上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We already have given it too much thought. Let's throw it out to the dump
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.28,1:01:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看猫会不会去舔\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and see if the cat licks it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.74,1:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 猫会不会去舔？  - 对\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- The cat licks it up? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.81,1:01:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看外面暗成什么样了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look how dark it's gettin' out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.22,1:01:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打赌要有暴雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I bet we're gonna have a storm now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.29,1:01:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，真的好热\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, oh boy. It's really hot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.36,1:01:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，你从来不流汗吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pardon me, but...don't you ever sweat?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.46,1:01:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我不流汗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.96,1:01:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，我在想...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen. I...I was wonderin' if...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.57,1:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许...我们该再投一次票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe...maybe we should take another vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.60,1:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，太棒了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.90,1:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们能坚持下去，跳个舞来点小吃。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe we can follow this one up with a little dancing and refreshments!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.01,1:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 主席先生？  - 我没有问题。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Mr.Foreman? - Well, that's OK with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.11,1:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人不愿意投票吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyone doesn't wanna vote?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.12,1:02:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嘿，够了。  - 什么？对不起\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Hey, come on. - What? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.42,1:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们应该公开投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think we ought to have an open ballot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.85,1:02:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出自己的投票，你知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Call out our votes, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.02,1:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们看看谁是什么立场\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's see who stands where.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.21,1:02:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听着挺公平\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, that sounds fair to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.73,1:02:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人反对吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyone object?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.46,1:02:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好。我按陪审员编号来叫。一号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. I'll call off your jury numbers. One?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.43,1:02:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，是我。我投有罪。二号?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, that's me. I vote guilty. Two?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.14,1:02:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.97,1:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number three?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.84,1:02:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.74,1:02:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number four?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.15,1:02:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.62,1:02:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number five?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.52,1:02:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.65,1:02:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number six?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.62,1:02:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.82,1:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number seven?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.93,1:02:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.56,1:02:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number eight?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.70,1:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.60,1:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number nine?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.78,1:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.54,1:02:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number ten?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.97,1:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.54,1:02:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number eleven?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.67,1:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.74,1:03:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number twelve?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.08,1:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二号？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Number twelve!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.51,1:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.99,1:03:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在票数是六比六\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The vote is now six to six.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.12,1:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，我们现在要打加时了，对吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, yeah, yeah. And we go into extra innings here, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.20,1:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六比六!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Six to six!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.73,1:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们说，你们之中有些人一定是失心疯了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm telling you, some of you people in here must be out of your minds.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.30,1:03:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的孩子！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A kid like that!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.94,1:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他是什么样的孩子跟这件事无关。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think the kind of boy he is has anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.51,1:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该用事实决定案子。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The facts are supposing to determine the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.52,1:03:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少拿那一套来唬我!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.76,1:03:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我厌倦了事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm sick and tired of facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.93,1:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以想怎么歪曲就怎么歪曲它，明白我的意思吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can twist 'em any way you like. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.71,1:03:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是这位先生一直强调的观点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's exactly the point this gentleman has been making.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.22,1:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，你一直扯着嗓门喊叫...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean, you keep shouting at the top of your lungs
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.25,1:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我能年轻几岁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to be a few years younger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.00,1:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人害得我...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That man gets on my...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.63,1:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这里真热，对吧？  - 你要喝点水吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- My, it's hot in here, isn't it? - Want a drink of water?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.36,1:03:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不，谢谢。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, no. Thanks. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.98,1:04:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下雨了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's gonna rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.91,1:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道呢，牛人？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, how'd you figure that out, killer?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.35,1:04:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会改变投票？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How come you changed your vote?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.48,1:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过在我看来有可疑之处。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It just seemed there was room for doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.15,1:04:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是没什么立场，你知道。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You haven't got a leg to stand on. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.95,1:04:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不那么认为。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.49,1:04:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多的细节并没有查清楚\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}A lot of details never came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.17,1:04:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对，祝你好运\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.66,1:04:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来了。你跟其他人一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on. You're like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.02,1:04:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想的太多，被弄迷糊了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You think too much, you get mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.36,1:04:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解我的意思吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.57,1:04:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，听着，我认为你没有权利...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, listen. I don't think you have any right to...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.57,1:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大嘴巴\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Loudmouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.52,1:05:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这雨下的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look at that come down, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.43,1:05:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.44,1:05:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我想起之前遇到的一场暴雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}this reminds me of a storm we had last...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.57,1:05:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十一月的事吗？我不知道。可能是吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Was it November? I don't know. Something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.10,1:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是一场大暴雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was quite a storm we had.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.95,1:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好在球赛中间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was right in the middle of a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.44,1:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们落后 六比七，但是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We were behind -seven to six, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.71,1:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正要持球推进，刚完成一次拦截。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We'd just started to move the ball, made a tackle.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.22,1:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备切往右边，斜线插入\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was gonna cut right in, slash through,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.27,1:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斜线右边，切入\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}slashed right in, cut right through...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.72,1:06:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有个孩子史莱特利\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We had this kid-Slattery.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.12,1:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是头牛。真正的公牛\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was an ox. A real ox.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.59,1:06:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望再有一个跟他一样的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I wish I had another one just like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.36,1:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了告诉你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.30,1:06:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是安德鲁·麦柯克高中的助理主教练\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm the assistant head coach at Andrew J McCorkle High School.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.07,1:06:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在皇后区\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's out in Queens.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.07,1:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，我们推进得很好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And anyway... we're starting to move along real nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.87,1:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道，他们的防线分开了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, their whole line is just... just comin' apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.51,1:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就开始下雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And it starts to come down,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.55,1:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾盆大雨，跟这场一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}cats and dogs, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.25,1:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是，刷...下来了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Just... whoosh! You know, right down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.25,1:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是要人命，你知道吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, it was murder, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓，我差点叫骂开了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I swear, I...I nearly bawled.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.28,1:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...我们无处施展\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Just... We couldn't go nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.91,1:07:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个电扇是怎么一回事？怎么会...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, what is it with this fan here? How come...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.33,1:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是跟电灯同一个开关\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Must have been on the same switch with the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.30,1:07:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情开始好转了，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, things are lookin' up here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.13,1:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.37,1:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，好多了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.22,1:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两分\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey! Two points.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.46,1:07:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去过花园广场吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You guys ever go to the Garden?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.66,1:07:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么做真的是太蠢了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's a damn stupid thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.83,1:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起。我...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.98,1:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.00,1:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.57,1:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得如何？平分。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, how do you like it? Even-steven.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.26,1:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当吃惊，是吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pretty surprising, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.44,1:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.68,1:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的事，那高个儿，叫什么来着，想要钓我上钩？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That...business before, when that tall guy, what's his name was tryin' to bait me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.81,1:08:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那无法证明什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That doesn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.12,1:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个很容易激动的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm a pretty excitable person
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.49,1:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，他想干吗？说我是公众复仇者，虐待狂。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where does he come off calling me a public avenger, a sadist?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.89,1:08:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都得买他的账\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyone in his right mind would blow his stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.33,1:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是想引我上钩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He was just tryin' to bait me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.70,1:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做的太好了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He did an excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.47,1:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你们我的想法，我们什么也达不成。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll tell you what I think, we're going nowhere here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.77,1:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备现在去庭上，宣布本案将成为悬判\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm ready to walk into court and declare a hung jury.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.09,1:08:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事继续谈下去没有意义\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's no point in this thing going on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.88,1:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我也同意\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, I go for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.51,1:08:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们告诉法官 把那孩子交给另外12个人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's take this to the judge Let the kid take his chance with 12 other guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.40,1:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为法官不会接受悬判\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The judge won't accept a hung jury.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.39,1:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这呆了很久了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We haven't been here long.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.72,1:08:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们走着瞧吧  - 我不支持那样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Well, let's find out. - I am not in favour of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.92,1:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，这孩子在另一个陪审团手里没机会，你知道的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, this kid wouldn't stand a chance with another jury, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.39,1:08:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，我们无解了。没人会改变投票。我们就这样办吧。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, we're hung. Nobody's gonna change his vote. Let's take this out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.33,1:08:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你仍然觉得没有可疑之处？  - 没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Still no room for reasonable doubt? - No. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.00,1:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Pardon.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.32,1:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你不完全了解“合理怀疑”这个术语\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe you don't fully understand the term "reasonable doubt".
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.20,1:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么我不了解？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean, I don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.37,1:09:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天，这家伙怎么这样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, how do you like this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.45,1:09:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们说，他们都一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm tellin' you, they're all alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.91,1:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来到这里忙着讨生活。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They come over here and run into a life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.71,1:09:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气都没喘匀，就急着告诉我们该怎么办\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Before they can take a breath they're telling us how to run the show.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.52,1:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天，这家伙傲慢自大！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, the arrogance of this guy!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.42,1:09:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。我们停止争执两分钟\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. Let's stop the arguing for about two minutes in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.96,1:09:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁有建设性的意见要说？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, who's got something constructive to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.56,1:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一些话想说，如果你们各位不介意的话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to go over something, if you gentlemen don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.23,1:09:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点对检方非常重要，就是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}An important point for the prosecution was the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.24,1:09:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子声称案发时他在电影院里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}after the boy claimed he'd been at the movies when the killing took place...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.74,1:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后他不记得那部电影及其中演员的名字\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he couldn't remember the names of the movies or who starred in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.84,1:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生几次提过这点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This gentleman has made that point sevaral times.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.54,1:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确。这是那男孩提供的唯一不在场证明\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's correct. It's the only alibi the boy offered
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.71,1:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他完全没法回忆任何细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and he himself couldn't back it up with any details at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.52,1:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站在那男孩的处境想想\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Put youself on the boy's place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.05,1:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得可以记起细节吗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}do you think you could remember details...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.85,1:09:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被自己的父亲打了巴掌后的心烦意乱中\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}after an upsetting experience such as being slapped by your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.36,1:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可以，只要有些特别的细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think so, if there were any special details to remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.59,1:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子记不起看过电影的名字\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy couldn't remember the name of the movies he saw
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.55,1:10:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那晚上他不在那\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}because he wasn't there that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.30,1:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据警方证词，那孩子在公寓的厨房接受探员询问\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}According to the police testimony, the boy was questioned by the detectives in the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.20,1:10:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他父亲的尸体还躺在卧室地板上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}while the body of his father was lying on the floor in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.27,1:10:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你在那种情形下还想起细节吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you think you could remember details on those certain stances
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.82,1:10:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.37,1:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巨大的精神压力下？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Under great emotional stress?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.83,1:10:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巨大的精神压力下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Under great emotional stress.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.01,1:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在法庭上正确记起了电影的名字和演出明星。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He remembered them correctly in court the names of the pictures and the stars played in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.38,1:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对。他的律师费尽力气才引他说出来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yes. His lawyer took great pains to bring that out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.95,1:10:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有3个月时间来回想，从案发到接受审判那天。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He had three months from the night of murder to the day of the trial in which to memorise them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.02,1:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个律师要查出某个影院某个晚上在放映什么并不难。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not difficult for a lawyer to find out what played at a particula theator on a particular night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.66,1:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我采信谋杀发生后警察询问那男孩的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll take the testimony the policemen took from the boy right after the murder...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.50,1:10:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时他记不起电影的任何事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}when he couldn't remember a thing about the movies,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.91,1:10:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论有巨大精神压力与否。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}great emotional stress or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.17,1:10:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你一个私人问题\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to ask you a personal question.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.67,1:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.40,1:10:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你在哪里？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.16,1:10:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在家里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was home.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.64,1:10:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天晚上呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How about the night before that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.84,1:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，这算什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.31,1:10:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.78,1:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我8:30下班，直接回家上床了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I left the office at 8.30 and went straight home and to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.28,1:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前天晚上呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And the night before that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.71,1:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...星期二晚上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That was...Tuesday night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.65,1:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥牌之夜，我去打桥牌了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The bridge tournament. I played bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.78,1:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一晚上呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Monday night?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.82,1:11:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想到1954年的新年夜时，通知我一声。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}When you get to New Year's Eve 1954, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.19,1:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一晚上？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Monday night?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.33,1:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一晚上...我妻子和我去看电影\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Monday night... my wife and I went to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.59,1:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看了什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.44,1:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《红圈》。是一部聪明的侦探片。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The Scarlet Circle. It's a very clever whodunit.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.77,1:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 第二部是什么呢?  - 是...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- What was the second feature? - The...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.21,1:11:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一会儿就告诉你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll tell you in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.98,1:11:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《杰出的...什么太太》\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The Remarkable Mrs...Something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.82,1:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宾布里奇太太。《杰出的宾布里奇太太》\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Mrs.Bainbridge. The Remarkable Mrs.Bainbridge
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.55,1:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过那个，它叫做《令人惊讶的宾布里奇太太》\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I saw that. It's called The Amazing Mrs Bainbridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.69,1:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对。《令人惊讶的宾布里奇太太》，我想是的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yes. The Amazing Mrs Bainbridge, I think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.96,1:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《令人惊讶的宾布里奇太太》里有谁呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who was in The Amazing Mrs Bainbridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.63,1:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭芭拉...隆格\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Barbara...Long,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.61,1:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她是个漂亮的黑美人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think it was a dark, very pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.94,1:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林德或隆格，差不多那样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ling or...Long. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.37,1:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who else?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.77,1:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有听过他们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'd never heard of them before.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.71,1:11:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一部低成本的二线电影，名不见经传\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It was a very inexpensive second feature, with unknown...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.18,1:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你并没有承受极大的情绪压力，对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And you weren't under an emotional stress, were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.12,1:12:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有，我没有\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.89,1:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想观点已经清楚了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think the point is made.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.73,1:12:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的重点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Big point.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.56,1:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以说到舌头拖地\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can talk till your tongue is draggin' on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.77,1:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子还是有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.57,1:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解我意思吗，我的朋友？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Know what I mean, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.07,1:12:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你还有喉糖吗?  - 全吃完了，我的朋友\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- You got those cough drops? - They're all gone, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.54,1:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计，看看这雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, boy. Look at that rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.45,1:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的球赛完了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There goes your ball game.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.14,1:12:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是一场阵雨\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's only a shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.65,1:12:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说，他们会盖住内野的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Besides, they got the infield covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.15,1:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说，我能看看那把刀吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Say, could I see that knife a second, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.59,1:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是六比六平手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, we're still tied up six to six.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.13,1:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁有建议吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who's got a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.19,1:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6点过5分了。去吃点晚饭吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's 5 after 6. Let's get some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.25,1:12:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不如等到7点，再过一小时？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why don't we wait till 7 o'clock? Give it another hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.63,1:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有意见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.10,1:12:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件事想说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's something I'd like to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.44,1:12:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，自从我们卡住了，它就一直着困扰我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean it's been bothering me a little as long as we're stuck...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.01,1:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于这个刀刺的伤口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There was this whole business about the stab wound
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.71,1:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及它怎么造成的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and how it was made.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.21,1:13:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的角度向下，你知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The downward angle of it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.71,1:13:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我说，我们要再开始这个。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't tell me that we're gonna start with that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.79,1:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经讨论过一遍又一遍\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They've been over it and over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.40,1:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他们讨论过，但我就是搞不懂\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I know they did, but I don't go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.75,1:13:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子五尺七寸高\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy was five feet seven inches tall.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.33,1:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他父亲是六尺二寸\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}His father was six two.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.06,1:13:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有七寸的差异\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's a difference of seven inches.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.32,1:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是件很难办到的事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's very awkward thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.51,1:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往下刺一个比你高半尺的人的胸部\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to stab downinto the chest of someone over half a foot taller.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.78,1:13:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那给我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.20,1:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你们示范。哪位起来\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll give you a demonstration. Somebody get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.08,1:13:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你们看好，因为我不想再做一遍。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I want you to watch this, because I don't wanna have to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.59,1:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让自己矮上6到7寸，好吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll make myself about six or seven inches shorter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.38,1:13:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了。可能再低点。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's about right. Maybe a little more.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.94,1:13:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，再低一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, a little more.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.76,1:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦...没人会受伤\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now...nobody's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.03,1:14:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.43,1:14:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，没有人会受伤\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Right. Nobody hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.51,1:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这样去刺...比我高的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, this is the way I'd stab a man who was...taller than I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.48,1:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个角度 往下插入\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look at the angle. Down and in.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.15,1:14:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是做法。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And this is the way it was done.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.14,1:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我我错了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now tell me I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.62,1:14:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往下插入，我想没有争议\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Down and in. I guess there's no argument.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.42,1:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，好吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hold on, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.06,1:14:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它给我。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Will you give me that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.86,1:14:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊，我恨透这些事了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Boy, I hate these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.93,1:14:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你见过持刀斗殴吗？  - 没有\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Did you ever see a knife fight? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.63,1:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你呢？  - 没有\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- You? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.30,1:14:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有人见过持刀斗殴吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anybody here ever see a knife fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.27,1:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.54,1:14:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道，我的烂出身\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know, on my back stoop,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.34,1:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街对面，后院里。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}the lot across the street, back yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.51,1:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社区里很多弹簧折刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Switchblades came with the neighbourhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.28,1:14:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑的是我以前没想到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Funny I never thought of it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.70,1:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是因为努力要忘记那些事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I guess you try to forget those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.21,1:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么使用弹簧折刀？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you use a switchblade?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.57,1:14:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝不会这样用它\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, you'd never use it like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.42,1:14:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看，换手损失了太多时间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}See, you'd lose too much time switching hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.56,1:14:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的。下手持握\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here's how. Underhand.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.53,1:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何用过折叠刀的人 都不会用别的方式握持\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anyone who's ever used switchknife wouldn't handle it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.10,1:15:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你确定?  - 我确定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Are you sure? - I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.68,1:15:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此他们才做成这样打开\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's why they're made to open like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.35,1:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说那男孩用刀相当熟练\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy was pretty handy with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.20,1:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他杀死他父亲 会造成那样的伤口吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You think he could have made the wound that killed his father?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.41,1:15:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。他有经验\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. Not with the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.30,1:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子握持这些东西的经验\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}he got all his life handling these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.44,1:15:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉他会下手握持\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I feel he'd have gone for him underhand.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.56,1:15:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.85,1:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那父亲被杀时你在房间里吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Were you there when the farther was killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.85,1:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。其他人也不在场\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. Neither was anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.85,1:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我们说这些莫名其妙的话干吗？我不相信\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What are you giving us this mumbo jumbo for? I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.22,1:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你无法判定 那男孩能或不能造成什么样的伤口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't think you can tell what kind of wound the boy might or might not have made...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.79,1:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅因为他知道怎么握刀\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}simply because he knew how to handle a knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.16,1:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.60,1:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.62,1:15:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么你不知道？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.90,1:15:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.74,1:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.84,1:15:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道其他人是怎么样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know about the rest of 'em,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.06,1:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经厌倦了这种叽叽喳喳进进退退。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but I'm gettin' tired of this yakety-yakkin' back and forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.51,1:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子我们没出路\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's gettin' us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.11,1:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我要打破局面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So I guess I'll have to break it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.28,1:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm changin' my vote to not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.88,1:15:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.38,1:16:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了，我受够了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You heard me. I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.32,1:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思受够了？那不是回答\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean you've had enough? That's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.62,1:16:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，你管好你自己，你知道吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, you just take care of yourself. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.78,1:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说得对。那不是回答\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's right. That's not an answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.90,1:16:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个什么样的人?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What kind of a man are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.98,1:16:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原先坐在这里 和其他人一样投有罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You have sat here and voted guilty with everyone else
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.31,1:16:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有什么棒球票在你口袋里热得发烫\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}because there are some baseball tickets burning a hole in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.51,1:16:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你改了投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now you have changed your vote
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.21,1:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你说厌倦了这些讨论\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}because you say you're sick of all the talking?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.51,1:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说，兄弟\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, listen, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.22,1:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁告诉你你有权...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Who tells you that you have the right
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.64,1:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样玩弄一个人的生命?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}to play like this with a man's life?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.12,1:16:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你不在乎吗？ - 等一下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't you care? -Now, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.72,1:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这样跟我说话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can't talk like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.21,1:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以这样跟你说话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I can talk like that to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.73,1:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If you want to vote not guilty,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.86,1:16:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须是因为你相信这人无罪,\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}do it because you are convinced the man is not guilty...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.26,1:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是因为你受够了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}not because you've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.10,1:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你觉得他有罪，就那样投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And if you think he is guilty, then vote that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.00,1:16:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你没胆去做你认为是对的事吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Or don't you have the guts to do what you think is right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.97,1:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 听我说  - 有罪还是无罪?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Now, listen... - Guilty or not guilty?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.11,1:16:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了，无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I told you. Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.31,1:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.31,1:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，我不必...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, I don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.05,1:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须。说出来。为什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You do have to. Say it. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.25,1:17:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不认为他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I...I don't think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.16,1:17:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求再次投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I want another vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.72,1:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的。要求再次投票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, that's another vote called for.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.57,1:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想最快的办法是举手。有人反对吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I guess the quickest way is a show of hands. Anyone object?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.44,1:17:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，认为无罪的 请举手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, all those voting not guilty, raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.34,1:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One, two, three, four, five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.25,1:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}eight.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.09,1:17:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.76,1:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为有罪的，请举手\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All those voting guilty, raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.03,1:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.57,1:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,票数是九比三支持无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, the vote's nine to three in favour of acquittal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.07,1:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞不懂你们这些人!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't understand you people!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.24,1:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们不断提出那些吹毛求疵的细节\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean all these picky little points you keep bringing up,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.83,1:18:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意义都没有!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}they don't mean nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.14,1:18:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们见过那孩子，跟我一样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You saw this kid just like I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.11,1:18:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我说你们相信 刀不见了的假故事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna tell me you believe that phoney story about losing the knife
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.58,1:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有关于电影的那些事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and those business about being at the movies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.72,1:18:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道这些人如何说谎。他们生来如此\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, you know how these people lie. It's born in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.85,1:18:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说，搞什么鬼。不必我来告诉你们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean what the heck. I don't have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.78,1:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道什么是真相！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They don't know what the truth is!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.87,1:18:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有，我告诉你们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And let me tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.94,1:18:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也不需要什么真正的理由就会杀人。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They don't need any real big reason to kill someone, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.96,1:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用，先生。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.43,1:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们喝醉了，他们都是真正的烂酒鬼，全都是。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They get drunk. They're real big drinkers, all of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.83,1:18:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你知道。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know that
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.70,1:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后，砰，有人倒在水沟里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Someone's lying in the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.08,1:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人怪他们。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody's blaming 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.20,1:18:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是这样，天性。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's the way they are by nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.21,1:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我的意思吗？暴力\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You know what I mean? Violent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.40,1:18:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.81,1:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对人命看得不如我们那么重。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Human life don't mean as much to them as it does to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.81,1:18:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们时刻在醉酒 打架\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They're lushing it up and fighting all the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.21,1:18:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人死了，那就死了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and if somebody gets killed, somebody gets killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.11,1:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不在乎!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They don't care!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.29,1:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，他们也有好的地方。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure, there's some good things about 'em, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.74,1:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看，我是第一个说这话的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, I'm the first one to say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.52,1:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识一对夫妇还不错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've known a couple who were OK
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.23,1:18:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是例外。懂我的意思吧？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but that's the exception. you know what i mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.26,1:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的大多数，就像是没有感情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Most of 'em, it's like they have no feelings!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.65,1:18:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们什么事都做得出来！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.01,1:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.07,1:19:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在告诉你们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.75,1:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们正在犯下大错，你们这些人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're making a big mistake, you people.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.87,1:19:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是骗子。我知道，我了解他们全部\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This kid is a liar. I know it. I know all about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.48,1:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说。他们不好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen to me. They're no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.95,1:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们中没有一个人有一点好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's not a one of 'em who's any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.85,1:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧，我说，这，这怎么一回事？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Look, I mean...what...what's happening in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.85,1:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说出我的想法，你们...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I speak my piece, and you...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.29,1:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.36,1:19:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受审的这孩子，他是个典型\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This kid on trial here. His type.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.56,1:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们不了解他们吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, don't you know about them?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.87,1:19:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里...这里有危险\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's a... There's a danger here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.53,1:19:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人很危险\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}These people are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.73,1:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们...野蛮\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}They're... wild.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.78,1:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.78,1:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.98,1:19:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.28,1:19:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，坐下，别再开口了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, sit down and don't open your mouth again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.99,1:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候...我告诉你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Some of the time...I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.23,1:20:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种事情上要排除个人偏见总是很难的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's always difficult to keep personal prejudice out of a thing like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.82,1:20:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论你从哪里入手，偏见总是遮蔽真相\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Wherever you run into it, prejudice always obscures the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.34,1:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不真的知道真相是什么\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't really know what the truth is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.01,1:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想任何人都不会真的知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't suppose anybody will ever really know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.01,1:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们九个人现在似乎觉得被告是无辜的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nine of us now seem to feel that the defendant is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.11,1:20:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们不过是在赌可能性\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But we're just gambling on probabilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.41,1:20:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许错了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We may be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.22,1:21:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许在放走一个有罪的人，我不知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We may be trying to let a guilty man go free. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.09,1:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人真的知道。但我们有合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Nobody really can. But we have a reasonable doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.73,1:21:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们的制度中非常有价值的东西\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And that's something that's very valuable in our system.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.56,1:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哪个陪审团能判决一个人有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No jury can declare a man guilty
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.46,1:21:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非十分确定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}unless it's sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.47,1:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们九个\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We nine...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.15,1:21:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不理解你们三个为什么还那么确定\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}can't understand how you three are still so sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.44,1:21:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你们能告诉我们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe you can tell us.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.82,1:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来试试\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.88,1:21:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你提出了一些极好的观点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You've made some excellent points,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.58,1:21:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我仍然相信 那男孩犯有谋杀罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but I still believe the boy is guilty on murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.62,1:21:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有两个原因\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have two reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.35,1:21:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一：对街那个女人给出的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}One: The evidence given by the woman across the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.54,1:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她实际上看到了谋杀实施\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}who actually saw the murder committed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.12,1:21:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来 那是最重要的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's the most important testimony.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.80,1:21:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二：她描述了刺杀过程的事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And two: The fact that she described the stabbing
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.44,1:21:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她看到那男孩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}by saying she saw the boy
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.50,1:21:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂高举过头 往他父亲的胸口刺下\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}raise his arm over his head and stab down into the father's chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.87,1:21:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看见他做了，错误的持刀法\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She saw him do it, the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.09,1:21:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.37,1:21:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来谈一谈这女人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's talk about this woman for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.64,1:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说当晚她大约在11点上床\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She said she went to bed about eleven o'clock that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.95,1:22:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的床临着窗户，她躺着就可以往外看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Her bed was next to the window, and she could look out while lying down
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.62,1:22:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接看到对街那男孩的房间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and see directly into the boy's room across the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.72,1:22:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她翻来覆去一个多小时 睡不着\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She tossed and turned for over an hour unable to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.39,1:22:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后她转向窗户 大约在12点过10分\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Finally, she turned toward the window at about 10 minutes after 12,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.73,1:22:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往外看的时候\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and as she looked out
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.40,1:22:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看到杀人 透过经过的电车车窗\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}she saw the killing through the windows of a passing el train.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.97,1:22:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说在凶杀发生后 立刻就没了灯光\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She said the lights went out immediately after the killing
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.70,1:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她清楚地看到那男孩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but that she got a good look at the boy
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.05,1:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺向他父亲的动作\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}in the act of stabbing his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.58,1:22:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我所见，这是不可动摇的证词\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}As far as I can see it, this is unshakeable testimony.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.11,1:22:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个案子就这样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, that's the whole case.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.06,1:22:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.05,1:22:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.72,1:22:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.09,1:22:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多证词要筛查\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So much evidence to sift.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.99,1:22:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个相当复杂的事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This is a pretty complicated business.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.06,1:22:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白讲，我看不出你怎么能投无罪票\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Frankly, I don't see how you can vote for acquittal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.03,1:22:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要安排这样的证词并不容易\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not so easy to arrange the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.60,1:22:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以抛开所有其他证据！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Throw out all the other evidence!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.38,1:23:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人看到他做了！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The woman saw him do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.70,1:23:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要别的什么呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.24,1:23:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯，也许...  - 我们来投票吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Well, maybe... - Let's vote on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.14,1:23:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，再度要求投票。有人反对吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK, there's another vote called for. Anyone object?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.35,1:23:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。我改变投票。他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}All right. I'm changing my vote. He's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.65,1:23:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别人吗？票数是八比四\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Anybody else? The vote is eight to four.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.02,1:23:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这就让你个人如此得意洋洋，这一票？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why is this such a personal triumph for you, this one vote?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.59,1:23:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好。我说我们是悬判。我说我们就这样告诉法官吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. I say we're a hung jury. I say we take it in to the judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.23,1:23:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这办法如何？我想听到争辩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How about it? I wanna hear arguments.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.20,1:23:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你，你是领头挑事的，这办法如何？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You, you're the leader of the cause. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.70,1:23:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再过一遍\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Let's go over it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.56,1:23:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经过了一遍了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We've been over it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.51,1:23:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个穿法兰绒外衣的男孩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The boy in the grey flannel suit
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.36,1:23:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个网球一样前后蹦来蹦去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}is bouncin' back and forth like a tennis ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.51,1:23:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要这么低级\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's no point in getting nasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.27,1:23:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不断地挑起争议\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You keep trying to turn this into a contest.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.42,1:23:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.85,1:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们应该谈谈 设一个时间限制\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe we can talk about setting some kind of time limit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.96,1:23:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对。时间一到我们就结案，嗯？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Yeah. Once around for the deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.89,1:23:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是...6点一刻\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's... a quarter after six.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.65,1:23:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前有人提过7点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Someone before mentioned seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.86,1:24:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到那个时间点 我们也许就开始讨论\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's a point at which we might begin to discuss the question
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.51,1:24:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是否定为悬判的问题\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}whether we're a hung jury or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.64,1:24:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉不好吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't you feel well?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.60,1:24:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉很好，谢谢你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I feel perfectly well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.61,1:24:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚说到7点是个合理的时间...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was saying seven o'clock would be a reasonable time...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.61,1:24:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问那个的原因，是因为\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The reason I asked that was because
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.22,1:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在按摩你的鼻子，就像...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}you were rubbing your nose like...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.32,1:24:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，对不起打断你了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'm sorry for interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.93,1:24:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的动作让我想起了一件事\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But you made a gesture that reminded me of something.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.02,1:24:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在试着订出规则，你不介意吧\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm trying to settle something here. Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.26,1:24:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这很重要\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, I think this is important.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.53,1:24:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.23,1:24:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在。我相信你会原谅我这么说，不过...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, then. I'm sure you'll pardon me for this, but
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.03,1:24:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想你为什么 要那样按摩你的鼻子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was wondering why you rub your nose like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.20,1:24:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧，行吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.74,1:24:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻我是在跟坐在你旁边的这位先生说话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}At this point I happen to be talking to the gentleman sitting next to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.94,1:24:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要那样按摩你的鼻子?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now, why were you rubbing your nose like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.51,1:24:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果跟你有关系的话\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}If it's any of your business,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.37,1:24:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按摩它 是因为它让我有点不舒服\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I was rubbing it because it bothers me a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.68,1:24:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，对不起。那是...因为你的眼镜吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I'm sorry. Is it...is it because of your eyeglasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.52,1:24:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.95,1:24:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们可以谈别的了吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Now could we get on to something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.02,1:24:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼镜造成那两个深印子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Your eyeglasses made those two deep impressions
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.72,1:25:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在鼻梁侧面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}on the sides of your nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.71,1:25:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前没有注意到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I hadn't noticed that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.84,1:25:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定挺烦人的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That must be annoying.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.43,1:25:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很烦人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It is very annoying.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.53,1:25:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不了解那种感觉\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I wouldn't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.50,1:25:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没戴过眼镜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I've never worn eyeglasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.80,1:25:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20 20\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}20 20
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.44,1:25:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着，你能不能放过这些验光师的事？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, will you come on already with the optometrist bit?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.28,1:25:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个作证说看见凶杀的女人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The woman who testified that she saw the killing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.95,1:25:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有同样的印子 在鼻梁侧面\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}had those same marks on the sides of her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.45,1:25:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的个天！他说的对\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Holy smoke! He's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.45,1:25:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.29,1:25:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一点时间...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Just give me a minute...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.41,1:25:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把话说完\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}and I'll be finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.39,1:25:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道其他人是否注意到她\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know if anyone else noticed that about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.36,1:25:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我没想到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I didn't think of it then,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.85,1:25:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直在琢磨她的脸，在我脑海里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}but I've been going over her face...in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.33,1:25:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也有这样的印子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She had those same marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.15,1:25:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在法庭上不停按摩它们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She kept rubbing them in court.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.17,1:25:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的对。她的确多次那么做\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}He's right. She did do that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.61,1:25:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人大约 45岁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This woman was about 45 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.41,1:25:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她非常努力让自己像35岁\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She was making a tremendous effort to look 35.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.47,1:26:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次在公众面前露脸\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}For her first public appearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.71,1:26:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓妆，染头发\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Heavy make-up. Dyed hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.16,1:26:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻女孩才会穿的崭新衣服\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Brand-new clothes that should have been worn by a younger woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.06,1:26:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有戴眼镜。女人常那么做\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No glasses. Well, women do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.84,1:26:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能不能 对她的心态有所了解\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}See if you can get a mental picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.47,1:26:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思，没戴眼镜？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you mean, no glasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.11,1:26:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道她戴不戴眼镜？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know whether she wore glasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.70,1:26:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为她按摩鼻子吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Just cos she was rubbin' her nose?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.09,1:26:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也有那种印子。我看见了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She had those marks. I saw 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.35,1:26:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎样？你觉得那有什么意义？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So? What do you think that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.03,1:26:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着。我烦透了你的吼叫\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Listen, I'm getting so sick of your yellin'...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.81,1:26:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了。算了。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Come on. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.31,1:26:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，听着，他说的对\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey, listen. Listen, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.50,1:26:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看到了。我是最靠近她的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I saw them too. I was the closest one to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.95,1:26:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有这些东西，在鼻子边上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She had these things on the side of her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.69,1:26:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫什么？在边上\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What you call them? on the side
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.12,1:26:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想表达什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What point are you makin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.82,1:26:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她染了头发，鼻子上有印子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She had dyed hair, marks on her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.42,1:26:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么意义？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.14,1:26:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些印子可能是除了眼镜以外其他东西造成的吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Could those marks be made by anything other than eyeglasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.83,1:26:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。不可能\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. They couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.14,1:26:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没看到什么印子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I didn't see any marks!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.81,1:26:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.82,1:26:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪，我之前没有想到这一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Strange, but I didn't think about it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.21,1:27:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个律师呢？他为什么不说什么？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about the lawyer? Why didn't the lawyer say something?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.88,1:27:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有12个人专注此案\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There are twelve people in here concentrating on this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.64,1:27:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们中11个人也没有想到\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Eleven of us didn't think of it either.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.65,1:27:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么地方检察官呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about the district attorney?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.45,1:27:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他会玩这种花招吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You think he'd pull a trick like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.02,1:27:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她作证时不戴眼镜？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Have her testify without her glasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.86,1:27:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从没见过不喜欢戴眼镜的女人吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Ever see a woman who won't wear glasses
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.46,1:27:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为觉得它会让她难看\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}because they spoil her looks?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.43,1:27:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧。她鼻子上有印子\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}OK. She had marks on her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.53,1:27:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认这一点\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm givin' you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.15,1:27:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜造成的，对吧?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}From glasses, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.30,1:27:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想戴着出门\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She didn't wanna wear 'em out of the house
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.69,1:27:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会觉得她很漂亮\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}so people'd think she's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.71,1:27:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她看到 那孩子杀死他父亲时\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But when she saw this kid killin' his father,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.96,1:27:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她待在房里，一个人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}she was in the house alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.31,1:27:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.51,1:27:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上床会戴着眼镜吗?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you wear glasses when you go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.78,1:27:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不。我不会\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.12,1:27:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人会戴着眼镜上床\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No one wears eyeglasses to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.20,1:27:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以合理地假设\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's logical to assume that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.54,1:27:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在床上并没有戴眼镜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}she wasn't wearing them in bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.95,1:27:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻来覆去想睡着\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Tossing and turning, trying to full asleep
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.93,1:27:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.13,1:27:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道，我猜测\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. I'm guessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.30,1:27:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还猜测她往窗外看去时，可能并没有戴眼镜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm also guessing that she didn't put them on when she looked out of the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.00,1:27:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还作证说 她往外看时 凶杀正好发生\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She testified the killing took place just as she looked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.34,1:27:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯关着，一两秒内她没有时间待戴上眼镜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The lights went off. a slip secend later She couldn't have time to put them on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.01,1:28:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 等一下  - 还有另一个猜测\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}- Wait a secend. -Here's another guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.87,1:28:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她真的认为 她看到了那男孩杀死他父亲\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe she honestly thought she saw the boy kill his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.43,1:28:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说她只看到个人影。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I say she only saw a blur.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.01,1:28:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道她看到了什么?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know what she saw?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.09,1:28:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会知道那么多事？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How does he know all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.88,1:28:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道 她戴的是哪种眼镜?\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know what glasses she wore?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.75,1:28:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是太阳镜！或许她是远视!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Maybe they were sunglasses! Maybe she was far-sighted!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.35,1:28:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你怎么会知道？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.76,1:28:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道 那个女人的视力现在有疑问\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I only know the woman's eyesight is in question now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.12,1:28:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她得有办法辨识出60尺外的人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}She had to be able to identify a person 60 feet away,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.98,1:28:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚，不戴眼镜\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}at night, without glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.83,1:28:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能靠这样的证据 让一个人送死\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can't send someone off to die on evidence like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.12,1:28:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，少来这一套\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Aw, don't give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.64,1:28:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得那女人可能犯错吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Don't you think the women might have made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.65,1:28:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.77,1:28:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's not possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.98,1:28:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，那是不可能的\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.81,1:28:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有可能吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.85,1:28:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.69,1:28:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为他有罪吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you think he's guilty?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.39,1:28:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I think he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.16,1:28:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.70,1:29:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.20,1:29:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被说服了。无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm convinced. Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.30,1:29:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么了？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.38,1:29:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在有了合理的怀疑\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I have a reasonable doubt now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.26,1:29:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一比一\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Eleven to one.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.94,1:29:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它所有证据呢？ \N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about all the other evidence?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.64,1:29:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西...那把刀，整个事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What about all that stuff? The...the knife? The whole business?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.08,1:29:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过我们可以抛开其它的证据\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, you said we could throw out all the other evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.79,1:29:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，我们现在怎么办？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.09,1:29:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落单了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.16,1:29:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎自己是不是落单\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I don't care whether I'm alone or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.44,1:29:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的权利\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's my right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.77,1:29:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的权利\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}It's your right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.95,1:29:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要什么？我说他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, what do you want? I say he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.05,1:29:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要听听你的争辩\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We want to hear your arguments.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.15,1:29:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们说过了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I gave you my arguments.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.62,1:30:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有被说服。我们想再听一次\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're not convinced. We want to hear them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.36,1:30:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们花多少时间都行\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We have as much time as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.10,1:30:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的东西，每一样在法庭上的东西\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Everything-every single thing that took place in that courtroom
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.92,1:30:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意思是每一样，都说他有罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I mean everything, says he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.91,1:30:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为呢？我是白痴什么的吗？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What do you think? I'm an idiot or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.81,1:30:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么不采信那个老人\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Why don't you take that stuff about the old man
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.42,1:30:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人住在那里 听到了所有事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}who lived there and heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.85,1:30:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那把刀的事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Or this business about the knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.35,1:30:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？就因为他们发现另一把完全一样的？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What? Because they found another one exactly like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.86,1:30:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老人看到他了！就在那，楼梯上。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The old man saw him! Right there, on the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.33,1:30:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了多少秒钟有什么区别？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's the difference how many seconds it was?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.03,1:30:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一样事情\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Every single thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.50,1:30:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀从他口袋的破洞掉了出去\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}The knife fallin' through a hole in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.90,1:30:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能证明他没有走到门口\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You can't prove he didn't get to the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.34,1:30:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然你，你能花很多时间蹒跚走过房间\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Sure, you can take all the time, hobble around the room
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.10,1:30:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你无法证明！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}But you can't prove it!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.58,1:30:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于电车是怎么回事？还有电影？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And what about this business of the el? And the movies?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.02,1:31:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有谎话的话 那就是了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}There's a phoney deal if I ever heard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.16,1:31:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们赌五千块  我会记得我看过的电影\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'll bet you $5,000 I'd remember the movies I saw.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.53,1:31:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你们\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm tellin' you,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.34,1:31:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事实都遭到了扭曲，被反转！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}everything that's gone on has been twisted and turned!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.53,1:31:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个眼镜的事情？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This business with the glasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.80,1:31:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道当时她没有戴眼镜？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}How do you know she didn't have 'em on?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.61,1:31:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人在公开法庭作证了！\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}This woman testified in open court!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.64,1:31:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有听到那孩子的喊叫声\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}And what about hearin' the kid yell?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.51,1:31:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你们，我这里有全部事实\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm tellin' ya, I've got all the facts here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.82,1:31:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.15,1:31:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样。整个事情就这样。\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well that's it. That's the whole case.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.86,1:31:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.73,1:31:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话啊!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Say something!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.97,1:31:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这一群狠心的混蛋\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You lousy bunch of bleedin' hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.14,1:32:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们恐吓不了我\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}You're not gonna intimidate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.35,1:32:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚持我的主张\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}I'm entitled to my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.22,1:32:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堕落的孩子...你毁了自己的一生!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Rotten kids... You work your life out!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.67,1:32:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}No...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.34,1:32:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.55,1:32:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无罪\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.96,1:32:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们准备好了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}We're ready now.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.04,1:34:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在测量走路时间的场景里）
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.44,1:34:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（实际用时是32秒，不是他说的41秒）
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.44,1:34:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（哥掐过表，你也可以试试）
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.04,1:34:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.32,1:34:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.99,1:34:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴维斯\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Davis.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.45,1:34:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫迈卡德\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}My name's McCardle.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.99,1:35:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，再见了\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}Well, so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.69,1:35:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\c&Hffffff&\fs11\fn微软雅黑}So long.
